; zoom: 1; color: #343131; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13px;\">&nbsp; &nbsp;Genit&iacute;v: bez č&iacute;chsi (cudz&iacute;ch)</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0.86em 0px 1.3em; padding: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #343131; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13px;\">&nbsp; &nbsp;Dat&iacute;v: d&aacute;m č&iacute;msi (cudz&iacute;m)</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0.86em 0px 1.3em; padding: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #343131; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13px;\">&nbsp; &nbsp;Akuzat&iacute;v: vid&iacute;m č&iacute;chsi, vid&iacute;m čiesi, vid&iacute;m čiesi (cudz&iacute;ch, cudzie, cudzie)</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0.86em 0px 1.3em; padding: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #343131; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13px;\">&nbsp; &nbsp;Lok&aacute;l: o&nbsp;č&iacute;chsi (cudz&iacute;ch)</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0.86em 0px 1.3em; padding: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #343131; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13px;\">&nbsp; &nbsp;In&scaron;trument&aacute;l: s č&iacute;misi (cudz&iacute;mi)</p>');
INSERT INTO `referaty` (`referat_id`, `user_id`, `category_id`, `title`, `created_at`, `skola`, `content`) VALUES
(18, 3, 2, 'Číslovky', '2024-01-24 15:33:16', 'ZŠ', '<p style=\"margin: 0.86em 0px 1.3em; padding: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #343131; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13px;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; zoom: 1;\">Charakteristika č&iacute;sloviek</strong></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0.86em 0px 1.3em; padding: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #343131; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13px;\">Č&iacute;slovky s&uacute; plnov&yacute;znamov&yacute;, ohybn&yacute; slovn&yacute; druh, ktor&yacute; určuje počet, poradie a&nbsp;množstvo os&ocirc;b , zvierat, vec&iacute;, javov, miest, du&scaron;evn&yacute;ch stavov. V&nbsp;slovenčine znač&iacute;me č&iacute;slovky č&iacute;slom 4. V&nbsp;slovenčine sa na ne p&yacute;tame ot&aacute;zkami &nbsp;Koľko?, Koľk&eacute;?, Koľk&yacute;?, Ktor&yacute;?, Ktor&aacute;?, Ktor&eacute;?</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0.86em 0px 1.3em; padding: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #343131; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13px;\"><em style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; zoom: 1;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; zoom: 1;\">Pri niektor&yacute;ch č&iacute;slovk&aacute;ch sa neurčuj&uacute; gramatick&eacute; kateg&oacute;rie a&nbsp;vzor.</strong></em></p>\r\n<h4 style=\"margin: 1.3em 0px 0px; padding: 0px; zoom: 1; font-weight: normal; line-height: 1.3em; font-size: 1.5em; color: #343131; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; zoom: 1;\">Delenie č&iacute;sloviek:</strong></h4>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0.86em 0px 1.3em; padding: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #343131; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13px;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; zoom: 1;\">A)&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;Z&aacute;kladn&eacute;:&nbsp;</strong>jeden, dva, tri, &scaron;tyri, p&auml;ť, &scaron;esť, sedem, osem, dev&auml;ť, desať....</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0.86em 0px 1.3em; padding: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #343131; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13px;\"><em style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; zoom: 1;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; zoom: 1;\">&nbsp; &nbsp;Pozor:</strong>&nbsp;Z&aacute;kladn&eacute; č&iacute;slovky 21, 31, 41, 51,61, 71, 81, 91.... sa v&nbsp;množnom č&iacute;sle (plur&aacute;li) neoh&yacute;baj&uacute;.</em></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0.86em 0px 1.3em; padding: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #343131; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13px;\"><em style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; zoom: 1;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; zoom: 1;\">&nbsp; &nbsp;Pr&iacute;klad:</strong>&nbsp;bolo tam dvadsaťjeden žien, vid&iacute;m dvadsaťjeden žien, bez dvadsaťjeden žien</em></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0.86em 0px 1.3em; padding: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #343131; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13px;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; zoom: 1;\">B)&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;R&aacute;dov&eacute;:&nbsp;</strong>prv&yacute;, druh&yacute;, tret&iacute;, &scaron;tvrt&yacute;, piaty, &scaron;iesty, siedmy, &ocirc;smy, deviaty, desiaty...</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0.86em 0px 1.3em; padding: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #343131; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13px;\"><em style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; zoom: 1;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; zoom: 1;\">&nbsp; &nbsp;Pozor:</strong>&nbsp;Radov&eacute; č&iacute;slovky sa skloňuj&uacute; podľa vzoru pekn&yacute; a&nbsp;cudz&iacute;.</em></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0.86em 0px 1.3em; padding: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #343131; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13px;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; zoom: 1;\">C)&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;N&aacute;sobn&eacute;:&nbsp;</strong>jedenkr&aacute;t, dvakr&aacute;t, trikr&aacute;t, &scaron;tyrikr&aacute;t, p&auml;ťkr&aacute;t, &scaron;esťkr&aacute;t, sedemkr&aacute;t, osemkr&aacute;t, dev&auml;ťkr&aacute;t, desaťkr&aacute;t....</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0.86em 0px 1.3em; padding: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #343131; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13px;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; zoom: 1;\">D)&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;Skupinov&eacute;:</strong>&nbsp;tento druh č&iacute;sloviek m&aacute; podobu pr&iacute;davn&yacute;ch mien a&nbsp;pr&iacute;sloviek.</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0.86em 0px 1.3em; padding: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #343131; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13px;\"><em style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; zoom: 1;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; zoom: 1;\">&nbsp; &nbsp;Pr&iacute;klady skupinov&yacute;ch č&iacute;sloviek:</strong>&nbsp;jednak&yacute;- jednako, mnohorak&yacute;- mnohorako</em></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0.86em 0px 1.3em; padding: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #343131; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13px;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; zoom: 1;\">E)&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;Určit&eacute; č&iacute;slovky:</strong>&nbsp;určuje presn&yacute; počet, množstvo a&nbsp;poradie</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0.86em 0px 1.3em; padding: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #343131; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13px;\"><em style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; zoom: 1;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; zoom: 1;\">&nbsp; &nbsp;Pr&iacute;klady určit&yacute;ch č&iacute;sloviek:</strong>&nbsp;jeden, dva, prv&yacute;, druh&yacute;, jedenkr&aacute;t, dvakr&aacute;t, jednak&yacute;, dvojak&yacute;</em></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0.86em 0px 1.3em; padding: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #343131; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13px;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; zoom: 1;\">F)&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;Neurčite č&iacute;slovky:</strong>&nbsp;neurčuj&uacute; presn&yacute; počet, množstvo a&nbsp;poradie</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0.86em 0px 1.3em; padding: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #343131; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13px;\"><em style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; zoom: 1;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; zoom: 1;\">&nbsp; &nbsp;Pr&iacute;klady neurčit&yacute;ch č&iacute;sloviek:</strong>&nbsp;m&aacute;lo, veľa, mnohorak&yacute;, mnoho</em></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0.86em 0px 1.3em; padding: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #343131; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13px;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h4 style=\"margin: 1.3em 0px 0px; padding: 0px; zoom: 1; font-weight: normal; line-height: 1.3em; font-size: 1.5em; color: #343131; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; zoom: 1;\">Gramatick&eacute; kateg&oacute;rie č&iacute;sloviek:</strong></h4>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0.86em 0px 1.3em; padding: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #343131; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13px;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; zoom: 1;\">1.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;P&aacute;d:&nbsp;</strong>Nominat&iacute;v (Kto?, Čo?), Genit&iacute;v (Koho?, Čoho?), Dat&iacute;v (Komu?, Čomu?), Akuzat&iacute;v (Koho?, Čo?), Lok&aacute;l&nbsp; (Kom?, Čom), In&scaron;trument&aacute;l (K&yacute;m?, Č&iacute;m)</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0.86em 0px 1.3em; padding: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #343131; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13px;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; zoom: 1;\">2.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;Vzor:</strong>&nbsp;medzi vzory č&iacute;sloviek patria jeden, dva, tri, &scaron;tyri, p&auml;ť, mesto, stroj, pekn&yacute;, cudz&iacute;, žena</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0.86em 0px 1.3em; padding: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #343131; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13px;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; zoom: 1;\">3.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;Č&iacute;slo:&nbsp;</strong>medzi č&iacute;sla č&iacute;sloviek patria jednotn&eacute; č&iacute;slo (singul&aacute;r) a&nbsp;množn&eacute; č&iacute;slo (plur&aacute;l)</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0.86em 0px 1.3em; padding: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #343131; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13px;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; zoom: 1;\">4.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;Rod:</strong>&nbsp;medzi rody č&iacute;sloviek patria mužsk&yacute;, žensk&yacute; a&nbsp;stredn&yacute; rod.</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0.86em 0px 1.3em; padding: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #343131; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13px;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h4 style=\"margin: 1.3em 0px 0px; padding: 0px; zoom: 1; font-weight: normal; line-height: 1.3em; font-size: 1.5em; color: #343131; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; zoom: 1;\">Charakteristick&eacute; črty skloňovac&iacute;ch vzorov č&iacute;sloviek:</strong></h4>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0.86em 0px 1.3em; padding: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #343131; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13px;\"><em style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; zoom: 1;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; zoom: 1;\">1.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;Skloňovanie podľa vzorov jeden, dva, tri, &scaron;tyri</strong></em>&nbsp;-&nbsp;Podľa vzorov jeden, dva, tri, &scaron;tyri sa skloňuj&uacute; č&iacute;slovky jeden, dva, tri a&nbsp;&scaron;tyri.</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0.86em 0px 1.3em; padding: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #343131; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13px;\"><em style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; zoom: 1;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; zoom: 1;\">2.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;Skloňovanie podľa vzoru p&auml;ť -&nbsp;</strong></em>Podľa vzoru p&auml;ť sa skloňuj&uacute; v&scaron;etky z&aacute;kladn&eacute; č&iacute;slovky</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0.86em 0px 1.3em; padding: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #343131; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13px;\"><em style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; zoom: 1;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; zoom: 1;\">3.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;Skloňovanie podľa vzoru mesto -</strong></em>&nbsp;Podľa vzoru mesto sa skloňuj&uacute; v&scaron;etky č&iacute;slo zakončen&eacute; v&nbsp;nominat&iacute;ve singul&aacute;ru na o, napr. sto, jedno</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0.86em 0px 1.3em; padding: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #343131; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13px;\"><em style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; zoom: 1;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; zoom: 1;\">4.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;Skloňovanie podľa vzoru stroj -</strong></em>&nbsp;Podľa vzoru stroj sa skloňuj&uacute; v&scaron;etky č&iacute;slovky zakončen&eacute; v&nbsp;nominat&iacute;ve singul&aacute;ru&nbsp; na m&auml;kk&uacute; spoluhl&aacute;sku. Takou č&iacute;slovkou je tis&iacute;c.</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0.86em 0px 1.3em; padding: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #343131; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13px;\"><em style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; zoom: 1;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; zoom: 1;\">5.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;Skloňovanie podľa vzoru cudz&iacute; -&nbsp;</strong></em>Podľa vzoru cudz&iacute; sa skloňuj&uacute; v&scaron;etky č&iacute;slovky, ktor&eacute; pred končiacou samohl&aacute;skou &iacute; maj&uacute; m&auml;kk&uacute; spoluhl&aacute;skou. Takouto č&iacute;slovkou je radov&aacute; č&iacute;slovka tis&iacute;ci</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0.86em 0px 1.3em; padding: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #343131; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13px;\"><em style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; zoom: 1;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; zoom: 1;\">6.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;Skloňovanie podľa vzoru pekn&yacute; -</strong></em>&nbsp;Podľa vzoru pekn&yacute; sa skloňuj&uacute; v&scaron;etky č&iacute;slovky, ktor&eacute; v&nbsp;nominat&iacute;ve singul&aacute;ru&nbsp; pred končiacou samohl&aacute;skou &yacute; maj&uacute; tvrd&uacute; spoluhl&aacute;sku. Patria sem radov&eacute; č&iacute;slovky (prv&yacute;, druh&yacute;, tret&iacute;), skupinov&eacute; č&iacute;slovky ( jednak&yacute;, dvojak&yacute;, mnohorak&yacute;)</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0.86em 0px 1.3em; padding: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #343131; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13px;\"><em style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; zoom: 1;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; zoom: 1;\">7.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;Skloňovanie podľa vzoru žena -</strong></em>&nbsp;Podľa vzoru žena sa skloňuj&uacute; v&scaron;etky č&iacute;slovky zakončen&eacute; v&nbsp;nominat&iacute;ve singul&aacute;ru na a, tak&yacute;mi č&iacute;slovkami s&uacute; nula a&nbsp;miliarda</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0.86em 0px 1.3em; padding: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #343131; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13px;\"><em style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; zoom: 1;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; zoom: 1;\">8.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;Skloňovanie podľa vzoru dub -</strong></em>&nbsp;Podľa vzoru dub sa skloňuj&uacute; v&scaron;etky č&iacute;slovky, ktor&eacute; s&uacute; v&nbsp;nominat&iacute;ve singul&aacute;ru zakončen&eacute; na tvrd&uacute; spoluhl&aacute;sku. Takouto č&iacute;slovkou je mili&oacute;n, bili&oacute;n, trili&oacute;n &nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0.86em 0px 1.3em; padding: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #343131; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13px;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h4 style=\"margin: 1.3em 0px 0px; padding: 0px; zoom: 1; font-weight: normal; line-height: 1.3em; font-size: 1.5em; color: #343131; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; zoom: 1;\">Vyskloňovanie vzorov č&iacute;sloviek</strong></h4>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0.86em 0px 1.3em; padding: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #343131; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13px;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; zoom: 1;\">Č&iacute;slovka jeden</strong></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0.86em 0px 1.3em; padding: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #343131; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13px;\"><em style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; zoom: 1;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; zoom: 1;\">Singul&aacute;r:</strong></em></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0.86em 0px 1.3em; padding: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #343131; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13px;\">N:&nbsp;jeden chlap, jedna žena, jedno mesto,&nbsp;G:&nbsp;&nbsp;bez jedn&eacute;ho mesta, bez jednej ženy, bez jedn&eacute;ho mesta,&nbsp;D:&nbsp;d&aacute;m jedn&eacute;mu chlapovi , d&aacute;m jednej žene , d&aacute;m jedn&eacute;mu mestu ,&nbsp;A:&nbsp;vid&iacute;m jedn&eacute;ho chlapa, vid&iacute;m jednu ženu, vid&iacute;m jedno mesto,&nbsp;L:&nbsp;o&nbsp;jednom chlapovi, o&nbsp;jednej žene, o&nbsp;jednom meste,&nbsp;I:&nbsp;s&nbsp;jedn&yacute;m chlapom , s&nbsp;jednou ženou, s&nbsp;jedn&yacute;m mestom</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0.86em 0px 1.3em; padding: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #343131; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13px;\"><em style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; zoom: 1;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; zoom: 1;\">Plur&aacute;l:</strong></em></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0.86em 0px 1.3em; padding: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #343131; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13px;\">N:&nbsp;jedni chlapi, jedny ženy, jedny mest&aacute;,&nbsp;G:&nbsp;bez jedn&yacute;ch ( chlapov, žien, miest),&nbsp;D:&nbsp;d&aacute;m jedn&yacute;m ( chlapom, žen&aacute;m, mest&aacute;m),&nbsp;A:&nbsp;vid&iacute;m jedn&yacute;ch chlapov, vid&iacute;m jedny ženy, vid&iacute;m jedny mest&aacute;,&nbsp;L:&nbsp;o&nbsp;jedn&yacute;ch ( chlapoch, žen&aacute;ch, mest&aacute;ch),&nbsp;I:&nbsp;s&nbsp;jedn&yacute;mi (chlapmi, ženami, mestami</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0.86em 0px 1.3em; padding: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #343131; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13px;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0.86em 0px 1.3em; padding: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #343131; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13px;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; zoom: 1;\">Č&iacute;slovka dva</strong></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0.86em 0px 1.3em; padding: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #343131; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13px;\"><em style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; zoom: 1;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; zoom: 1;\">Singul&aacute;r:</strong></em></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0.86em 0px 1.3em; padding: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #343131; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13px;\"><em style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; zoom: 1;\">Pozor:&nbsp;Singul&aacute;r v&nbsp;č&iacute;slovke &nbsp;dva neexistuje!</em></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0.86em 0px 1.3em; padding: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #343131; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13px;\"><em style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; zoom: 1;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; zoom: 1;\">Plur&aacute;l:</strong></em></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0.86em 0px 1.3em; padding: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #343131; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13px;\">N:&nbsp;dvaja chlapi, dve ženy, dve mest&aacute;,&nbsp;G:&nbsp;bez dvoch ( chlapov, žien, miest),&nbsp;D:&nbsp;d&aacute;m dvom ( chlapom, žen&aacute;m, mest&aacute;m),&nbsp;A:&nbsp;vid&iacute;m dvoch chlapov, vid&iacute;m dve ženy, vid&iacute;m dve mest&aacute;,&nbsp;L:&nbsp;o&nbsp;dvoch ( chlapoch, žen&aacute;ch, mesta),&nbsp;I:&nbsp;s&nbsp;dvoma/ s&nbsp;dvomi ( chlapmi, ženami, mestami)</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0.86em 0px 1.3em; padding: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #343131; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13px;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0.86em 0px 1.3em; padding: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #343131; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13px;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; zoom: 1;\">Č&iacute;slovka tri</strong></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0.86em 0px 1.3em; padding: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #343131; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13px;\"><em style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; zoom: 1;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; zoom: 1;\">Singul&aacute;r:&nbsp;</strong></em></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0.86em 0px 1.3em; padding: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #343131; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13px;\"><em style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; zoom: 1;\">Pozor: Singul&aacute;r v č&iacute;slovke tri neexistuje!</em></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0.86em 0px 1.3em; padding: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #343131; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13px;\"><em style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; zoom: 1;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; zoom: 1;\">Plur&aacute;l:</strong></em></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0.86em 0px 1.3em; padding: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #343131; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13px;\">N:&nbsp;traja chlapi, tri ženy, tri mest&aacute;,&nbsp;G:&nbsp;bez troch ( chlapov, žien, miest),&nbsp;D:&nbsp;d&aacute;m trom ( chlapom, žen&aacute;m, mest&aacute;m),&nbsp;A:&nbsp;vid&iacute;m troch chlapov, vid&iacute;m tri ženy, vid&iacute;m tri mest&aacute;,&nbsp;L:&nbsp;o&nbsp;troch ( chlapoch, žen&aacute;ch, mest&aacute;ch),&nbsp;I:&nbsp;s&nbsp;tromi/troma ( chlapmi, ženami, mestami</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0.86em 0px 1.3em; padding: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #343131; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13px;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0.86em 0px 1.3em; padding: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #343131; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13px;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; zoom: 1;\">Č&iacute;slovka &nbsp;&scaron;tyri</strong></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0.86em 0px 1.3em; padding: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #343131; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13px;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; zoom: 1;\"><em style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; zoom: 1;\">Singul&aacute;r:</em></strong></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0.86em 0px 1.3em; padding: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #343131; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13px;\"><em style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; zoom: 1;\">Pozor: Singul&aacute;r v&nbsp;č&iacute;slovke &scaron;tyri neexistuje!</em></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0.86em 0px 1.3em; padding: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #343131; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13px;\"><em style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; zoom: 1;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; zoom: 1;\">Plur&aacute;l:</strong></em></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0.86em 0px 1.3em; padding: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #343131; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13px;\">N:&nbsp;&scaron;tyria chlapi, &scaron;tyri ženy, &scaron;tyri mest&aacute;.&nbsp;G:&nbsp;bez &scaron;tyroch (chlapov, žien, miest),&nbsp;D:&nbsp;d&aacute;m &scaron;tyrom (chlapom, žen&aacute;m, mest&aacute;m,&nbsp;A:&nbsp;vid&iacute;m &scaron;tyroch chlapov, vid&iacute;m &scaron;tyri ženy, vid&iacute;m &scaron;tyri mest&aacute;,&nbsp;L:&nbsp;&nbsp;o&nbsp;&scaron;tyroch (chlapoch, žen&aacute;ch, mest&aacute;ch,&nbsp;I:&nbsp;so &scaron;tyrmi (chlapmi, ženami, mestami)&nbsp;&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0.86em 0px 1.3em; padding: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #343131; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13px;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0.86em 0px 1.3em; padding: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #343131; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13px;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; zoom: 1;\">Č&iacute;slovka p&auml;ť</strong></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0.86em 0px 1.3em; padding: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #343131; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13px;\"><em style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; zoom: 1;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; zoom: 1;\">Singul&aacute;r:</strong></em></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0.86em 0px 1.3em; padding: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #343131; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13px;\"><em style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; zoom: 1;\">Pozor: Singul&aacute;r vo vzore p&auml;ť neexistuje!</em></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0.86em 0px 1.3em; padding: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #343131; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13px;\"><em style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; zoom: 1;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; zoom: 1;\">Plur&aacute;l:</strong></em></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0.86em 0px 1.3em; padding: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #343131; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13px;\">N:&nbsp;p&auml;ť (chlapov, žien, miest),&nbsp;G:&nbsp;bez piatich (chlapov, žien, miest),&nbsp;D:&nbsp;d&aacute;m piatim (chlapom, žen&aacute;m, mest&aacute;m),&nbsp;A:&nbsp;vid&iacute;m piatich chlapov, vid&iacute;m p&auml;ť žien, vid&iacute;m p&auml;ť miest,&nbsp;L:&nbsp;o&nbsp;piatich(chlapoch, žen&aacute;ch, mest&aacute;ch,&nbsp;I:&nbsp;s&nbsp;piatimi (chlapmi, ženami, mestami)</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0.86em 0px 1.3em; padding: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #343131; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13px;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0.86em 0px 1.3em; padding: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #343131; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13px;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; zoom: 1;\">Vzor mesto: Podľa vzoru mesto sa skloňuje z&aacute;kladn&aacute; č&iacute;slovka sto</strong></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0.86em 0px 1.3em; padding: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #343131; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13px;\"><em style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; zoom: 1;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; zoom: 1;\">Singul&aacute;r:</strong></em></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0.86em 0px 1.3em; padding: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #343131; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13px;\">N:&nbsp;sto (mesto),&nbsp;G:&nbsp;bez sta (mesta),&nbsp;D:&nbsp;d&aacute;m stu (d&aacute;m mestu),&nbsp;A:&nbsp;vid&iacute;m sto (vid&iacute;m mesto),&nbsp;L:&nbsp;o&nbsp;ste (o&nbsp;meste),&nbsp;I:&nbsp;so stom (s&nbsp;mestom)</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0.86em 0px 1.3em; padding: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #343131; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13px;\"><em style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; zoom: 1;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; zoom: 1;\">Plur&aacute;l:</strong></em></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0.86em 0px 1.3em; padding: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #343131; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13px;\">N:&nbsp;st&aacute; (mest&aacute;),&nbsp;G:&nbsp;&nbsp;bez sto,&nbsp;D:&nbsp;d&aacute;m st&aacute;m (mest&aacute;m),&nbsp;A:&nbsp;vid&iacute;m st&aacute; (vid&iacute;m mest&aacute;),&nbsp;L:&nbsp;o&nbsp;st&aacute;ch (o&nbsp;mest&aacute;ch,&nbsp;I:&nbsp;so stami (s&nbsp;mestami)</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0.86em 0px 1.3em; padding: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #343131; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13px;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0.86em 0px 1.3em; padding: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #343131; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13px;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; zoom: 1;\">Vzor stroj : Podľa vzoru stroj sa skloňuje z&aacute;kladn&aacute; č&iacute;slovka tis&iacute;c</strong></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0.86em 0px 1.3em; padding: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #343131; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13px;\"><em style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; zoom: 1;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; zoom: 1;\">Singul&aacute;r:</strong></em></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0.86em 0px 1.3em; padding: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #343131; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13px;\">N:&nbsp;tis&iacute;c (stroj),&nbsp;G:&nbsp;bez tis&iacute;ca (bez stroja),&nbsp;D:&nbsp;d&aacute;m tis&iacute;cu (d&aacute;m stroju),&nbsp;A:&nbsp;vid&iacute;m tis&iacute;c (vid&iacute;m stroj,&nbsp;L:&nbsp;o&nbsp;tis&iacute;ci (o&nbsp;stroji),&nbsp;I:&nbsp;s&nbsp;tis&iacute;com (so strojom)</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0.86em 0px 1.3em; padding: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #343131; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13px;\"><em style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; zoom: 1;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; zoom: 1;\">Plur&aacute;l:</strong></em></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0.86em 0px 1.3em; padding: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #343131; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13px;\">N:&nbsp;tis&iacute;ce,&nbsp;G:&nbsp;tis&iacute;c,&nbsp;D:&nbsp;tis&iacute;c,&nbsp;A:&nbsp;tis&iacute;ce,&nbsp;L:&nbsp;tis&iacute;c,&nbsp;I:&nbsp;tis&iacute;c&nbsp;&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0.86em 0px 1.3em; padding: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #343131; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13px;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0.86em 0px 1.3em; padding: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #343131; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13px;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; zoom: 1;\">Vzor cudz&iacute;:&nbsp;Podľa vzoru cudz&iacute; sa skloňuje radov&aacute; č&iacute;slovka tis&iacute;ci</strong></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0.86em 0px 1.3em; padding: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #343131; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13px;\"><em style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; zoom: 1;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; zoom: 1;\">Singul&aacute;r:</strong></em></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0.86em 0px 1.3em; padding: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #343131; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13px;\">N:&nbsp;tis&iacute;ci chlap, tis&iacute;ca žena, tis&iacute;ce mesto,&nbsp;G:&nbsp;bez tis&iacute;ceho chlapa, bez tis&iacute;cej ženy, bez tis&iacute;ceho mesta,&nbsp;D:&nbsp;d&aacute;m tis&iacute;cemu chlapovi, d&aacute;m tis&iacute;cej žene, d&aacute;m tis&iacute;cemu mestu,&nbsp;A:&nbsp;vid&iacute;m tis&iacute;ceho chlapa, vid&iacute;m tis&iacute;cu ženu, vid&iacute;m tis&iacute;ce mesto,&nbsp;L:&nbsp;o&nbsp;tis&iacute;com chlapovi, o&nbsp;tis&iacute;cej žene, o&nbsp;tis&iacute;com meste,&nbsp;I:&nbsp;s&nbsp;tis&iacute;cim chlapom, s&nbsp;tis&iacute;cou ženou, s&nbsp;tis&iacute;cim mestom</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0.86em 0px 1.3em; padding: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #343131; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13px;\"><em style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; zoom: 1;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; zoom: 1;\">Plur&aacute;l:</strong></em></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0.86em 0px 1.3em; padding: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #343131; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13px;\">N:&nbsp;tis&iacute;ci chlapi, tis&iacute;ce ženy, tis&iacute;ce mest&aacute;,&nbsp;G:&nbsp;bez tis&iacute;cich ( chlapov, žien, miest),&nbsp;D:&nbsp;d&aacute;m tis&iacute;cim ( chlapom, žen&aacute;m, mest&aacute;m),&nbsp;A:&nbsp;vid&iacute;m tis&iacute;cich chlapov, vid&iacute;m tis&iacute;ce ženy, vid&iacute;m tis&iacute;ce mest&aacute;,&nbsp;L:&nbsp;o&nbsp;tis&iacute;cich ( chlapov, žien, miest),&nbsp;I:&nbsp;s&nbsp;tis&iacute;cimi ( chlapmi, ženami , mestami)</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0.86em 0px 1.3em; padding: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #343131; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13px;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0.86em 0px 1.3em; padding: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #343131; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13px;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; zoom: 1;\">Vzor pekn&yacute;: Podľa vzoru pekn&yacute; sa skloňuj&uacute; r&aacute;dov&eacute; a&nbsp;skupinov&eacute; č&iacute;slovky</strong></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0.86em 0px 1.3em; padding: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #343131; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13px;\"><em style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; zoom: 1;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; zoom: 1;\">Singul&aacute;r:</strong></em></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0.86em 0px 1.3em; padding: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #343131; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13px;\">N:&nbsp;prv&yacute; chlap, prv&aacute; žena, prv&eacute; mesto,&nbsp;G:&nbsp;bez prv&eacute;ho chlapa, bez prvej ženy, bez prv&eacute;ho mesta,&nbsp;D:&nbsp;d&aacute;m prv&eacute;mu chlapovi, d&aacute;m prvej žene, d&aacute;m prv&eacute;mu mestu,&nbsp;A:&nbsp;vid&iacute;m prv&eacute;ho chlapa, vid&iacute;m prv&uacute; ženu, vid&iacute;m prv&eacute; mesto,&nbsp;L:&nbsp;&nbsp;o&nbsp;prvom chlapovi, o&nbsp;prvej žene, o&nbsp;prvom meste,&nbsp;I:&nbsp;s&nbsp;prv&yacute;m chlapom, s&nbsp;prvou ženou, s&nbsp;prv&yacute;m mestom</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0.86em 0px 1.3em; padding: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #343131; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13px;\"><em style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; zoom: 1;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; zoom: 1;\">Plur&aacute;l:</strong></em></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0.86em 0px 1.3em; padding: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #343131; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13px;\">N:&nbsp;prv&iacute; chlapi, prv&eacute; ženy , prv&eacute; mest&aacute;,&nbsp;G:&nbsp;bez prv&yacute;ch (chlapov, žien, miest),&nbsp;D:&nbsp;d&aacute;m prv&yacute;m (chlapom, žen&aacute;m, mest&aacute;m),&nbsp;A:&nbsp;vid&iacute;m prv&yacute;ch chlapov, vid&iacute;m prv&eacute; ženy, vid&iacute;m prv&eacute; mest&aacute;,&nbsp;L:&nbsp;o&nbsp;prv&yacute;ch (chlapoch, žen&aacute;ch, mest&aacute;ch),&nbsp;I:&nbsp;s&nbsp;prv&yacute;mi (chlapmi, ženami, mestami)&nbsp;&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0.86em 0px 1.3em; padding: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #343131; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13px;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0.86em 0px 1.3em; padding: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #343131; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13px;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; zoom: 1;\">Vzor žena: Podľa vzoru žena sa skloňuje č&iacute;slovka miliarda</strong></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0.86em 0px 1.3em; padding: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #343131; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13px;\"><em style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; zoom: 1;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; zoom: 1;\">Singul&aacute;r:</strong></em></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0.86em 0px 1.3em; padding: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #343131; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13px;\">N:&nbsp;miliarda (žena),&nbsp;G:&nbsp;bez miliardy (bez ženy),&nbsp;D:&nbsp;d&aacute;m miliarde (d&aacute;m žene),&nbsp;A:&nbsp;vid&iacute;m miliardu (vid&iacute;m ženu),&nbsp;L:&nbsp;o miliarde&nbsp; (o&nbsp;žene),&nbsp;I:&nbsp;s&nbsp;miliardou (so ženou)</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0.86em 0px 1.3em; padding: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #343131; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13px;\"><em style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; zoom: 1;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; zoom: 1;\">Plur&aacute;l:</strong></em></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0.86em 0px 1.3em; padding: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #343131; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13px;\">N: dve miliardy (dve ženy),&nbsp;G:&nbsp;bez mili&aacute;rd (bez žien),&nbsp;D:&nbsp;d&aacute;m miliard&aacute;m (d&aacute;m žen&aacute;m),&nbsp;A:&nbsp;vid&iacute;m dve miliardy (vid&iacute;m dve ženy),&nbsp;L:&nbsp;o&nbsp;miliard&aacute;ch (o&nbsp;žen&aacute;ch),&nbsp;I:&nbsp;s&nbsp;mili&aacute;rdami (so ženami)</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0.86em 0px 1.3em; padding: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #343131; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13px;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; zoom: 1;\">Vzor dub: Podľa vzoru dub sa skloňuj&uacute; č&iacute;slovky mili&oacute;n, bili&oacute;n, trili&oacute;n</strong></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0.86em 0px 1.3em; padding: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #343131; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13px;\"><em style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; zoom: 1;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; zoom: 1;\">Singul&aacute;r:</strong></em></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0.86em 0px 1.3em; padding: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #343131; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13px;\">N:&nbsp;mili&oacute;n (dub),&nbsp;G:&nbsp;bez mili&oacute;na (bez duba),&nbsp;D:&nbsp;d&aacute;m mili&oacute;nu (d&aacute;m dubu),&nbsp;A:&nbsp;vid&iacute;m mili&oacute;n (vid&iacute;m dub),&nbsp;L:&nbsp;o&nbsp;mili&oacute;ne (o&nbsp;dube),&nbsp;I:&nbsp;s&nbsp;mili&oacute;nom (s&nbsp;dubom)</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0.86em 0px 1.3em; padding: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #343131; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13px;\"><em style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; zoom: 1;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; zoom: 1;\">Plur&aacute;l:</strong></em></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0.86em 0px 1.3em; padding: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #343131; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13px;\">N: mili&oacute;ny (duby), G: bez mili&oacute;nov (bez dubov), D: d&aacute;m mili&oacute;nom (d&aacute;m dubom), A: vid&iacute;m mili&oacute;ny (vid&iacute;m duby), L: o mili&oacute;noch&nbsp; (o duboch), I: s mili&oacute;nmi (s dubmi)</p>'),
(19, 3, 2, 'Prídavné mená', '2024-01-24 15:33:41', 'ZŠ', '<p style=\"margin: 0.86em 0px 1.3em; padding: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #343131; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13px;\">-su plnovyznamove ohybne slova</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0.86em 0px 1.3em; padding: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #343131; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13px;\">Rozdelenie prid. mien akostne-daju sa stupnovat vztahove-vztahuju sa na nieco privlastnovacie-privlastnuje to niekomu alebo niecomu</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0.86em 0px 1.3em; padding: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #343131; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13px;\">Vzory prid. mien pekny cudzi otcov matkin p&aacute;v&iacute;</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0.86em 0px 1.3em; padding: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #343131; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13px;\">Stupnovanie prid. mien pravidelne nepravidelne-su len 5 :maly, velky, dobry, zly, pekny. opisne stupnovanie:horuca-menej horuca-najmenej horuca</p>'),
(20, 3, 2, 'Opis', '2024-01-24 15:34:35', 'ZŠ', '<p style=\"margin: 0.86em 0px 1.3em; padding: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #343131; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13px;\">Opis je jazykov&yacute; prejav, ktor&yacute;m sa maj&uacute; jednoducho a v&yacute;stižne vyjadriť hlavn&eacute; a podstatn&eacute; znaky zobrazovan&eacute;ho predmetu alebo javu. M&ocirc;že byť statick&yacute; (opisuje objekt v stave pokoja) alebo dynamick&yacute; (opisuje objekt v pohybe alebo opisuje n&aacute;slednosť činnosti pri v&yacute;robe niečoho &ndash; opis pracovn&eacute;ho postupu).<br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; zoom: 1;\" /><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; zoom: 1;\" />Ak sa nehybn&yacute; objekt opisuje tak, ako ho vn&iacute;ma pohybuj&uacute;ca sa osoba ide o opis s dejov&yacute;m r&aacute;mcom (dejov&yacute; opis). Je čast&yacute; v report&aacute;ži a v umeleckej literat&uacute;re.<br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; zoom: 1;\" /><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; zoom: 1;\" />Pri opise zložitej&scaron;ieho pr&iacute;stroja alebo pracovn&eacute;ho postupu b&yacute;va často zmie&scaron;an&yacute; &uacute;tvar statick&eacute;ho a dynamick&eacute;ho opisu (hybrid). Praktick&yacute; opis je jednoduch&yacute;, použ&iacute;va term&iacute;ny, ktor&eacute; m&ocirc;že pochopiť i laik.</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0.86em 0px 1.3em; padding: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #343131; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13px;\">Odborn&yacute; opis použ&iacute;va odborn&uacute; terminol&oacute;giu dan&eacute;ho oboru. Postoj autora je objekt&iacute;vny. Cieľom odborn&eacute;ho opisu je poučiť prij&iacute;mateľa o zobrazovanej veci. Použ&iacute;va dvojčlenn&eacute; vety a s&uacute;vetia (najm&auml; podraďovacie).</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0.86em 0px 1.3em; padding: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #343131; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13px;\">Umeleck&yacute; opis (n&aacute;ladov&yacute;) oboznamuje čitateľa s vlastnosťou spoločensk&yacute;ch a pr&iacute;rodn&yacute;ch javov, s vlastnosťami post&aacute;v. Využ&iacute;va podst. a pr&iacute;d. men&aacute; (statick&yacute;), sloves&aacute; (dynamick&yacute; opis) a r&ocirc;zne umeleck&eacute; prostriedky. Opis, ktor&yacute; vystihuje pr&iacute;značn&eacute; črty post&aacute;v, ich du&scaron;evn&eacute; i telesn&eacute; vlastnosti, sa naz&yacute;va charakteristikou.<br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; zoom: 1;\" /><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; zoom: 1;\" />Kompoz&iacute;cia opisu z&aacute;vis&iacute; od jeho funkcie. Kompozičn&yacute; postup m&ocirc;že byť r&ocirc;zny (opis zhora dolu, od podstatn&yacute;ch znakov k menej podstatn&yacute;m, od celku k častiam a pod.). Jazykov&eacute; prostriedky opisu: podstatn&eacute; men&aacute;, pr&iacute;d. men&aacute;, pr&iacute;slovky sp&ocirc;sobu a miery, sloves&aacute;, odborn&eacute; term&iacute;ny.<br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; zoom: 1;\" /><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; zoom: 1;\" />&Scaron;tyliz&aacute;cia opisu z&aacute;vis&iacute; od druhu opisu. V statickom, odbornom opise prevl&aacute;da menn&eacute; vyjadrovanie, trpn&yacute; rod (pas&iacute;vum) a polovetn&eacute; pr&iacute;časťov&eacute; kon&scaron;trukcie. V opise pracovn&eacute;ho postupu prevl&aacute;da slovesn&eacute; vyjadrovanie (v 2. os. pl. rozkazovacieho sp&ocirc;sobu alebo v 1. os. pl. oznamovacieho sp&ocirc;sobu). Je potrebn&eacute; použ&iacute;vať v jednom opise rovnak&uacute; slovesn&uacute; osobu a dodržiavať časov&uacute; n&aacute;slednosť činnost&iacute;. Cieľom opisu je poučiť prij&iacute;mateľa.</p>');
INSERT INTO `referaty` (`referat_id`, `user_id`, `category_id`, `title`, `created_at`, `skola`, `content`) VALUES
(21, 3, 2, 'Lexikológia', '2024-01-24 15:34:53', 'ZŠ', '<p style=\"margin: 0.86em 0px 1.3em; padding: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #343131; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13px;\">&ndash; n&aacute;uka o slovnej z&aacute;sobe, lexis = slovo, logos = n&aacute;uka, veda<br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; zoom: 1;\" />predmet sk&uacute;mania: SZ &ndash; lexika, vlastnosti slov a slovn&yacute;ch spojen&iacute; ako pomenovac&iacute;ch jednotiek, sk&uacute;manie vz&aacute;jomn&eacute;ho vzťahu t&yacute;chto jednotiek v syst&eacute;me slov. z&aacute;soby aj pri použit&iacute; v jazykovom prejave, určenie lexik&aacute;. v&yacute;znamu, vzťah v&yacute;znamu a pojmu.<br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; zoom: 1;\" /><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; zoom: 1;\" />Lexik&oacute;n = lexik&aacute;lny subsyst&eacute;m jazyka je vn&uacute;torne &scaron;trukt&uacute;rovan&yacute;, hierarchizovan&yacute; syst&eacute;m podsyst&eacute;mov, s&uacute;bor, kt. je otvoren&yacute;, t.j. prij&iacute;ma, adaptuje cudzie prvky, ale patr&iacute; sem aj odb. terminol&oacute;gia, ktor&aacute; st&aacute;le rastie. Jazykov&eacute; jednotky s&uacute; usporiadan&eacute; v tzv. čiastkov&yacute;ch syst&eacute;moch, v poliach, v mikrosyst&eacute;moch.<br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; zoom: 1;\" /><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; zoom: 1;\" />SZ slovenčiny = celon&aacute;rodn&yacute; jazyk. Jeho variety: spisovn&yacute; j., n&aacute;rečia, slang, argot, žarg&oacute;n<br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; zoom: 1;\" />spisovn&yacute; jazyk</p>\r\n<ul style=\"margin: 0.86em 0px 1.3em 1.3em; padding: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #343131; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13px;\">\r\n<li style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; zoom: 1;\">najd&ocirc;ležitej&scaron;ia forma n&aacute;rodn&eacute;ho jazyka</li>\r\n<li style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; zoom: 1;\">jazyk sloven. &scaron;koly, kn&iacute;h, nov&iacute;n, divadla, rozhlasu a TV</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0.86em 0px 1.3em; padding: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #343131; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13px;\">je v protiklade s:</p>\r\n<ul style=\"margin: 0.86em 0px 1.3em 1.3em; padding: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #343131; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13px;\">\r\n<li style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; zoom: 1;\">teritori&aacute;lnymi n&aacute;rečiami &ndash; osobitn&aacute; hl&aacute;skoslovn&aacute;, gramatick&aacute; a lexik&aacute;lna stavba:</li>\r\n<li style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; zoom: 1;\">z&aacute;padoslovensk&eacute;</li>\r\n<li style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; zoom: 1;\">stredoslovensk&eacute;</li>\r\n<li style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; zoom: 1;\">v&yacute;chodoslovensk&eacute;</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0.86em 0px 1.3em; padding: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #343131; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13px;\">soci&aacute;lnymi n&aacute;rečiami &ndash; reč rozlič. skup&iacute;n spojen&yacute;ch spoločn&yacute;mi z&aacute;ujmami, rovnakou činnosťou, profesiou (nemaj&uacute; vlastn&uacute; zvukov&uacute;, gramatick&uacute; a lexik&aacute;lnu stavbu, prepožičiavaj&uacute; si ju zo spisov. slovenčiny alebo z teritori&aacute;lnych n&aacute;reč&iacute;)</p>\r\n<ul style=\"margin: 0.86em 0px 1.3em 1.3em; padding: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #343131; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13px;\">\r\n<li style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; zoom: 1;\">slang (&scaron;tudentsk&yacute;, vojensk&yacute;, poľovn&iacute;cky)</li>\r\n<li style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; zoom: 1;\">argot</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0.86em 0px 1.3em; padding: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #343131; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13px;\">Z&aacute;kl. jednotka SZ: slovo.<br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; zoom: 1;\" />Slovo sa sk&uacute;ma z hľadiska:</p>\r\n<ol style=\"margin: 0.86em 0px 1.3em 1.5em; padding: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #343131; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13px;\">\r\n<li style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; zoom: 1;\">v&yacute;znamu,</li>\r\n<li style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; zoom: 1;\">miesta v celkovom syst&eacute;me lexiky,</li>\r\n<li style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; zoom: 1;\">p&ocirc;vodu,</li>\r\n<li style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; zoom: 1;\">gramatick&yacute;ch vlastnost&iacute;,</li>\r\n<li style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; zoom: 1;\">sf&eacute;ry použ&iacute;vania v komunik&aacute;cii,<br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; zoom: 1;\" />expres&iacute;vno-&scaron;tylistickej charakteristiky.</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0.86em 0px 1.3em; padding: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #343131; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13px;\">Akt&iacute;vna SZ = 5 &ndash; 10 tis. lexik&aacute;lnych jednotiek (jednotlivec ju použ&iacute;va v hovor. a p&iacute;san. prejavoch)<br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; zoom: 1;\" />Pas&iacute;vna SZ = 6x bohat&scaron;ia, v&auml;č&scaron;ia, v modernej SZ je asi mili&oacute;n lex. jednotiek, terminol&oacute;gia je najbohat&scaron;ia oblasť SZ (komunikant jej rozumie, ale ju akt&iacute;vne nepouž&iacute;va)<br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; zoom: 1;\" />Bernol&aacute;k, A.: Slow&aacute;r Slowensk&iacute;, Česko-Latinsko-Nemecko-Uhersk&iacute; (6-zv. preklad. 1825-27)</p>\r\n<h4 style=\"margin: 1.3em 0px 0px; padding: 0px; zoom: 1; font-weight: normal; line-height: 1.3em; font-size: 1.5em; color: #343131; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\">ČIASTKOV&Eacute; LEXIKOLOGICK&Eacute; DISCIPL&Iacute;NY<br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; zoom: 1;\" /><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; zoom: 1;\" />Členenie lexikol&oacute;gie:</h4>\r\n<ol style=\"margin: 0.86em 0px 1.3em 1.5em; padding: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #343131; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13px;\">\r\n<li style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; zoom: 1;\">syntagmatick&aacute; (kombinatorick&aacute;) &ndash; vzťahy medzi LX-ymi jednotkami zoskupen&yacute;mi v jednom syntakt. rade &ndash;line&aacute;rne</li>\r\n<li style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; zoom: 1;\">paradigmatick&aacute; &ndash; v&yacute;znamy LX-ych jednotiek, ich vzťahy vn&uacute;tri 1 LX-ej jednotky alebo medzi viacer&yacute;mi 1-v&yacute;zn. LX</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0.86em 0px 1.3em; padding: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #343131; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13px;\">jednotkami, alebo viacv&yacute;zn. LXJ-ami. Podľa predmetu sk&uacute;mania sa v jej r&aacute;mci rozli&scaron;uje:</p>\r\n<ul style=\"margin: 0.86em 0px 1.3em 1.3em; padding: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #343131; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13px;\">\r\n<li style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; zoom: 1;\">lexik&aacute;lna s&eacute;mantika,</li>\r\n<li style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; zoom: 1;\">onomaziol&oacute;gia,</li>\r\n<li style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; zoom: 1;\">derivatol&oacute;gia,</li>\r\n<li style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; zoom: 1;\">frazeol&oacute;gia,</li>\r\n<li style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; zoom: 1;\">terminol&oacute;gia,</li>\r\n<li style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; zoom: 1;\">onomastika,</li>\r\n<li style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; zoom: 1;\">lexikografia.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0.86em 0px 1.3em; padding: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #343131; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13px;\">lexik&aacute;lna s&eacute;mantika, semaziol&oacute;gia &ndash; metodologicky postupuje od formy k obsahu, zaober&aacute; sa v&yacute;znamom LJ-iek a v&yacute;znamov&yacute;mi vzťahmi.<br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; zoom: 1;\" /><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; zoom: 1;\" />onomaziol&oacute;gia &ndash; n&aacute;uka o pomenovaniach, patr&iacute; sem aj derivatol&oacute;gia - n&aacute;uka o tvoren&iacute; slov, ako s&uacute; utvoren&eacute; tie slov&aacute;, ktor&eacute; svojou form&aacute;lnou &scaron;trukt&uacute;rou naznačuj&uacute; svoj lexik&aacute;lny v&yacute;znam &ndash; tzv. slovotvorne motivovan&eacute; slov&aacute; (odvoden&eacute; i zložen&eacute; &ndash; 2/3 SZ), t. j. slov&aacute; tvoren&eacute; od in&yacute;ch slov zmenou ich morfematickej &scaron;trukt&uacute;ry.</p>\r\n<h4 style=\"margin: 1.3em 0px 0px; padding: 0px; zoom: 1; font-weight: normal; line-height: 1.3em; font-size: 1.5em; color: #343131; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\">Na z&aacute;klade &scaron;pecifick&yacute;ch čŕt sa vyčleňuje:</h4>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0.86em 0px 1.3em; padding: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #343131; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13px;\">frazeol&oacute;gia &ndash; n&aacute;uka o viaclovn&yacute;ch lexik&aacute;lnych jednotk&aacute;ch, ktor&eacute; s&uacute; napospol &scaron;tylisticky pr&iacute;znakov&eacute; (jestvuje viacero v&yacute;medzen&iacute; f-ie), v &scaron;ir&scaron;om ch&aacute;pan&iacute;:</p>\r\n<ul style=\"margin: 0.86em 0px 1.3em 1.3em; padding: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #343131; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13px;\">\r\n<li style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; zoom: 1;\">priame združen&eacute; pomenovania</li>\r\n<li style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; zoom: 1;\">nepriame pomenovania &ndash; frazeologick&eacute; jednotky</li>\r\n<li style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; zoom: 1;\">frazeologizovan&eacute; spojenia &ndash; ust&aacute;lenosť, nezameniteľnosť komponentov v lexik&aacute;lnom obsaden&iacute;, ne&uacute;pln&aacute; paradigma komponentov, v&yacute;skyt petrifikovan&yacute;ch a zastaran&yacute;ch v&yacute;razov a tvarov.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0.86em 0px 1.3em; padding: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #343131; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13px;\">terminol&oacute;gia &ndash; n&aacute;uka o odborn&yacute;ch term&iacute;noch</p>\r\n<ul style=\"margin: 0.86em 0px 1.3em 1.3em; padding: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #343131; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13px;\">\r\n<li style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; zoom: 1;\">z&aacute;kladn&eacute; vlastnosti</li>\r\n<li style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; zoom: 1;\">v&yacute;znam odborn&eacute;ho term&iacute;nu v porovnan&iacute; s neterminologick&yacute;m pomenovan&iacute;m</li>\r\n<li style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; zoom: 1;\">&scaron;trukt&uacute;ra odborn&yacute;ch term&iacute;nov</li>\r\n<li style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; zoom: 1;\">zdroje, ust&aacute;lenosť term&iacute;nov</li>\r\n<li style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; zoom: 1;\">terminologiz&aacute;cia a determinologiz&aacute;cia</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0.86em 0px 1.3em; padding: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #343131; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13px;\">onomastika &ndash; n&aacute;uka o vlastn&yacute;ch men&aacute;ch<br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; zoom: 1;\" /><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; zoom: 1;\" />lexikografia &ndash; n&aacute;uka o vedeckom zostavovan&iacute; slovn&iacute;kov (rozlič. druhy opisov. slovn&iacute;kov, typol&oacute;gia slovn., stavba hesiel, sp&ocirc;soby v&yacute;kladu, gram. a &scaron;tyl. charakter slov, exemplifik&aacute;cie)</p>\r\n<h4 style=\"margin: 1.3em 0px 0px; padding: 0px; zoom: 1; font-weight: normal; line-height: 1.3em; font-size: 1.5em; color: #343131; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\">LEXIK&Aacute;LNA ROVINA V POROVNAN&Iacute; S IN&Yacute;MI JAZYKOV&Yacute;MI ROVINAMI</h4>\r\n<ul style=\"margin: 0.86em 0px 1.3em 1.3em; padding: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #343131; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13px;\">\r\n<li style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; zoom: 1;\">zahŕňa viac prvkov, m&aacute; bohat&scaron;iu a rozmanitej&scaron;iu sieť vzťahov medzi prvkami</li>\r\n<li style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; zoom: 1;\">najbezprostrednej&scaron;ie spojen&aacute; s mimojazykovou skutočnosťou</li>\r\n<li style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; zoom: 1;\">prechodn&eacute; oblasti medzi rovinami:</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0.86em 0px 1.3em; padding: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #343131; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13px;\">tvorenie slov</p>\r\n<ul style=\"margin: 0.86em 0px 1.3em 1.3em; padding: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #343131; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13px;\">\r\n<li style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; zoom: 1;\">prepojenie lexik&aacute;lnej a morfologickej roviny: paralelnosť a totožnosť form&aacute;lnych prostriedkov: slov&aacute; i gramatick&eacute; tvary sa tvoria predponov&yacute;mi a pr&iacute;ponov&yacute;mi morf&eacute;mami, často sa t&aacute; ist&aacute; morf&eacute;ma využ&iacute;va na tvorenie slov i tvarov (konverzia: zl&yacute; &ndash; zlo, letieť &ndash; let &ndash; 0, žab-a &ndash; žab-&iacute;)</li>\r\n<li style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; zoom: 1;\">prepojenie lexik&aacute;lnej a syntaktickej roviny: paralelnosť vo vzťahoch medzi členmi syntagiem a komponentmi odvoden&eacute;ho slova alebo zložen&eacute;ho slova (X spieva &ndash; ten, kto spieva =spev&aacute;k, m&aacute; tvrd&uacute; hlavu &ndash; tvrdo-hlav-&yacute;)</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0.86em 0px 1.3em; padding: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #343131; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13px;\">oblasť viacslovn&yacute;ch pomenovan&iacute;, t. j. pomenovac&iacute;ch jednotiek zložen&yacute;ch z viac ako jedn&eacute;ho slova, ale vyjadruj&uacute;cich jeden celistv&yacute; v&yacute;znam</p>\r\n<ul style=\"margin: 0.86em 0px 1.3em 1.3em; padding: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #343131; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13px;\">\r\n<li style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; zoom: 1;\">prepojenie lexik&aacute;lnej a syntaktickej roviny: medzi slovami ako komponentmi pomenovan&iacute; sa zachov&aacute;vaj&uacute; syntaktick&eacute; vzťahy, realizuj&uacute; sa syntaktick&eacute; kon&scaron;trukcie, ale<br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; zoom: 1;\" />-v&yacute;znam spojen&iacute; je celistv&yacute;, nie je s&uacute;hrnom lexik&aacute;lnych v&yacute;znamov jednotliv&yacute;ch komponentov,<br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; zoom: 1;\" />-spojenia nemožno rozčleniť na men&scaron;ie jednotky, lebo by stratili alebo pozmenili svoj v&yacute;znam,<br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; zoom: 1;\" />-netvoria sa zakažd&yacute;m znovu, ale funguj&uacute; ako celok a maj&uacute; rovnak&uacute; hodnotu ako jednoslovn&eacute; pomenovania,</li>\r\n<li style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; zoom: 1;\">priame (združen&eacute; pomenovania) : vysok&aacute; pec, n&aacute;rodn&aacute; rada, skok o žrdi, kysličn&iacute;k uhličit&yacute;</li>\r\n<li style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; zoom: 1;\">nepriame metaforick&eacute; (frazeologick&eacute; jednotky): na nevydržanie, lansk&eacute; snehy, p&auml;sť na oko, vodiť za nos, vziať nohy na ple</li>\r\n</ul>'),
(22, 3, 3, 'Martin Kukučín-Neprebudený', '2024-01-24 15:35:28', 'ZŠ', '<div class=\"section\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #343131; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13px;\">\r\n<div class=\"obsah\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0.86em 0px 0px; zoom: 1;\">\r\n<h4 style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; zoom: 1; font-weight: normal; line-height: 1.3em; font-size: 1.5em;\">T&eacute;ma:</h4>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0.86em 0px 1.3em; padding: 0px; zoom: 1;\">Tragick&yacute; pr&iacute;beh du&scaron;evne zaostal&eacute;ho dedinsk&eacute;ho husiara Ondr&aacute;&scaron;a Machuľu, ktor&yacute; sa<br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; zoom: 1;\" />stal obeťou vyb&aacute;jenej l&aacute;sky k peknej gazdovskej dievčine Zuzke Bežanovie.</p>\r\n<h4 style=\"margin: 1.3em 0px 0px; padding: 0px; zoom: 1; font-weight: normal; line-height: 1.3em; font-size: 1.5em;\">Dej:</h4>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0.86em 0px 1.3em; padding: 0px; zoom: 1;\">Ondra&scaron; Machuľa, biedny tvor. Hlava veľk&aacute;, kryt&aacute; ostr&yacute;mi vlasmi, ktor&eacute; sa pon&aacute;&scaron;aj&uacute; na zvieraciu srsť, čelo n&iacute;zke, oči n&aacute;padne mal&eacute;, l&iacute;cne kosti vypukl&eacute;, nos rozpľa&scaron;ten&yacute; na kab&aacute;č a &uacute;sta &scaron;irok&eacute;. Postavu m&aacute; mal&uacute;, nevyvinut&uacute;, zhrben&uacute;. ľudia na neho s utrpen&iacute;m hľadia a chovaj&uacute; sa k nemu so &scaron;etrnosťou ako k mal&eacute;mu dieťaťu.</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0.86em 0px 1.3em; padding: 0px; zoom: 1;\">Len on s&aacute;m sa za mrz&aacute;ka nepoklad&aacute;, drž&iacute; sa za pekn&eacute;ho. Vie rozoznať, čo je pekn&eacute; a čo &scaron;kared&eacute;, no o svojej osobe s&uacute;di predpojato. Každ&yacute; ale r&aacute;d videl jeho hodn&yacute;ch, zn&aacute;&scaron;anliv&yacute;ch rodičov,ktor&yacute;ch ľutovali za ich nepodaren&eacute;ho syna. Ondr&aacute;&scaron;ova matka svojho syna veľmi milovala.<br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; zoom: 1;\" />Ondr&aacute;&scaron;a matersky riadila a vypr&aacute;vala do &scaron;koly. A chlapec sa dobre učil, pretože v ňom bola badať du&scaron;a, du&scaron;a ako u ostatn&yacute;ch, čo bolo jedinou potechou i odplatou starostlivej totke.</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0.86em 0px 1.3em; padding: 0px; zoom: 1;\">Ondr&aacute;&scaron;ov otec ale na svojho syna ani pozrieť nemohol, hľadal preto &uacute;ľavu v krčme. Napokon sa totka s manželom nepohodli a totka odi&scaron;la z domu k star&scaron;ej sestre. Po asi dvoch rokoch od chv&iacute;ľe, čo sa nepohodli, totka sa st&aacute;va vdovou.<br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; zoom: 1;\" />V jeden deň, kedy p&aacute;sol Ondr&aacute;&scaron; husi, mu Zuzka Bežanovie doniesla obed. Mala jasn&uacute; tv&aacute;r, červen&uacute; ako ruža.</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0.86em 0px 1.3em; padding: 0px; zoom: 1;\">Červen&aacute; pera odokr&yacute;vala dva rady bielych per&aacute;l. Pre Ondr&aacute;&scaron;a to bola stvoren&aacute; princezn&aacute;. Zuzka mu povie, že sa nepohodla s Janom D&uacute;bravovie, svoj&iacute;m n&aacute;padn&iacute;kom. To Ondr&aacute;&scaron; využije, vypočuje ju a dohodne sa s ňou na svadbe. No netu&scaron;&iacute;, že Zuzka to nemysl&iacute; v&aacute;žne a že sa stal obeťou jej samoľ&uacute;bosti. S radosťou to povie totke.</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0.86em 0px 1.3em; padding: 0px; zoom: 1;\">T&aacute; ho pravdaže odhov&aacute;ra, pretože si uvedomuje, že Zuzka Bežanovie sa chcela vždy vydať za J&aacute;na D&uacute;bravovie. Z&aacute;jde aj za jej matkou, ktor&aacute; je prekvapen&aacute; jej n&aacute;v&scaron;tevou. Ondr&aacute;&scaron; ale robil v&scaron;etky kroky k svadbe. Daroval Bežaňov&yacute;m najkraj&scaron;iu habarku a op&aacute;lku, ktor&eacute; s&aacute;m vyrobil, vyhnal im s&aacute;m husi z domu a zarobil si na vlnu, z ktorej si dal u&scaron;iť nohavice na svadbu. Za habarku a op&aacute;lku si nič nezobral, čo začalo tr&aacute;piť Bežanku.</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0.86em 0px 1.3em; padding: 0px; zoom: 1;\">Zavolala si Zuzku, prehovorila jej do du&scaron;e a doholi sa, že svadba s J&aacute;nom D&uacute;bravovie bude sk&ocirc;r. Ohl&aacute;&scaron;ky J&aacute;na D&uacute;bravovie so Zuzkou Bežanovie boli v dedine hlavnou t&eacute;mou po niekoľko t&yacute;ždňov. No Ondr&aacute;&scaron;ovi sa t&aacute;to spr&aacute;va ako jedin&eacute;mu nedostala do u&scaron;&iacute;. St&aacute;le si myslel, že on bude žen&iacute;chom. Dedinsk&yacute; krajč&iacute;r mu napokon u&scaron;il aj cifrovan&yacute; oblek na svadbu.</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0.86em 0px 1.3em; padding: 0px; zoom: 1;\">V deň svadby ho ale totka zavre do k&ocirc;lne a schov&aacute; pred n&iacute;m oblek. Ondr&aacute;&scaron; sa napokon z k&ocirc;lne pomocou sekery dostane, ale Zuzka a J&aacute;n D&uacute;bravovie s&uacute; už po sob&aacute;&scaron;i. Prich&aacute;dza na svadobn&uacute; veselicu, kde je veľmi dobr&aacute; n&aacute;lada. Ondr&aacute;&scaron;a ale neprijm&uacute; na tanec, z čoho je smutn&yacute; a s&aacute;m si ide sadn&uacute;ť do &scaron;opy. Neskoro v noci začne horieť.</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0.86em 0px 1.3em; padding: 0px; zoom: 1;\">Pri ohni jedin&eacute;ho n&aacute;jdu Ondr&aacute;&scaron;a, ktor&eacute;ho považuj&uacute; za podpaľača a keďže sa v&scaron;etci boja, že by im aj in&eacute; budovy zap&aacute;lil, poviažu ho. Nesk&ocirc;r sa o neho nezauj&iacute;maj&uacute;. Zastav&iacute; sa pri ňom len Zuzka, ale keďže Ondr&aacute;&scaron; cel&yacute; čas bl&uacute;zni, povie mu že už je vydat&aacute; za J&aacute;na D&uacute;bravovie. Ondr&aacute;&scaron; to pochop&iacute;, ale mysl&iacute; si, že na neho čakali a keď neprich&aacute;dzal, dali poslať po J&aacute;na.</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0.86em 0px 1.3em; padding: 0px; zoom: 1;\">Zuzka sa pok&uacute;&scaron;a vysvetliť mu, že na neho nečakali, no Ondr&aacute;&scaron; ju nepoč&uacute;val a myslel si svoje. Bežanka medzičasom ale zist&iacute;, že jej husi s&uacute; v horiacej ma&scaron;tali a chce ich zachr&aacute;niť. No strecha stodoly už bola celkom prehoren&aacute; a mohla už každ&uacute; chv&iacute;lu padn&uacute;ť. Zuzka Ondr&aacute;&scaron;a odviaže a ten sa vrhne do stodoly za husami. No husy sa mu už zachr&aacute;niť nepodar&iacute; a s&aacute;m v stodole zhor&iacute;. Ľudia v tom vidia trest bož&iacute; za podpalačstvo.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>'),
(23, 3, 3, 'Margita Figuli', '2024-01-24 15:35:46', 'ZŠ', '<h4 style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; zoom: 1; font-weight: normal; line-height: 1.3em; font-size: 1.5em; color: #343131; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\">Margita Figuli</h4>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0.86em 0px 1.3em; padding: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #343131; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13px;\">( 1909 - 1995 )</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0.86em 0px 1.3em; padding: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #343131; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13px;\">Patr&iacute; k hlavn&yacute;m predstaviteľom lyrizovanej pr&oacute;zy. Jej diela sa vyznačuj&uacute; bohat&yacute;mi lyrizačn&yacute;mi postupmi a metaforick&yacute;m &scaron;t&yacute;lom. Narodila sa v roku 1909 vo Vy&scaron;nom Kub&iacute;ne v roľn&iacute;ckej rodine. Po skončen&iacute; obchodnej akad&eacute;mie pracovala ako bankov&aacute; &uacute;radn&iacute;čka v Bratislave. Po vojne p&ocirc;sobila vo v&yacute;bore Zv&auml;zu slovensk&yacute;ch spisovateľov. Zomrela v Bratislave v roku 1995.</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0.86em 0px 1.3em; padding: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #343131; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13px;\">Do literat&uacute;ry vst&uacute;pila zbierkou noviel&nbsp;<strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; zoom: 1;\">Poku&scaron;enie</strong>&nbsp;( 1937). Najv&yacute;znamnej&scaron;&iacute;m dielom je rom&aacute;nov&aacute; novela&nbsp;<strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; zoom: 1;\">Tri ga&scaron;tanov&eacute; kone</strong>&nbsp;(1940). T&aacute;to novela patr&iacute; k najlep&scaron;&iacute;m dielam slovensk&eacute;ho naturizmu. Počas vojny nap&iacute;sala svoje najrozsiahlaj&scaron;ie dielo, historick&yacute; rom&aacute;n&nbsp;<strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; zoom: 1;\">Babylon</strong>&nbsp;( 1946). Ďal&scaron;ie dielo vydala Margite Figuli až po dlh&scaron;ej odmlke. Bol to biografick&yacute; rom&aacute;n Mladosť (1956). Zachytila v ňom svoje detstvo i život ľud&iacute; na chudobnej, ale kr&aacute;snej Orave počas rokov 1. svetovej vojny. Ďal&scaron;ie diela boli rom&aacute;ny&nbsp;<strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; zoom: 1;\">Ariadnina niť</strong>&nbsp;(1964) a&nbsp;<strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; zoom: 1;\">V&iacute;chor v n&aacute;s</strong>&nbsp;(1974).</p>'),
(24, 3, 3, 'Fraňo Kráľ - Čenkovej deti', '2024-01-24 15:36:02', 'ZŠ', '<p style=\"margin: 0.86em 0px 1.3em; padding: 0px; zoom: 1; font-size: 13px; letter-spacing: normal;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; zoom: 1;\">T&eacute;ma:</strong>&nbsp;Ťažk&yacute; život Zuzany Čenkovej a jej det&iacute;.</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0.86em 0px 1.3em; padding: 0px; zoom: 1; font-size: 13px; letter-spacing: normal;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; zoom: 1;\">Idea:</strong>&nbsp;Z&aacute;chrana det&iacute; za každ&uacute; cenu.</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0.86em 0px 1.3em; padding: 0px; zoom: 1; font-size: 13px; letter-spacing: normal;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; zoom: 1;\">&Uacute;tvar:</strong>&nbsp;Poviedka</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0.86em 0px 1.3em; padding: 0px; zoom: 1; font-size: 13px; letter-spacing: normal;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; zoom: 1;\">Kompozičn&yacute; postup:</strong>&nbsp;reťazovo, retrospekt&iacute;vne; vyskytuje sa tu ich a jej forma</p>\r\n<h4 style=\"margin: 1.3em 0px 0px; padding: 0px; zoom: 1; font-weight: normal; line-height: 1.3em; font-size: 1.5em; color: #343131; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\">F&aacute;zy dejovej v&yacute;stavby diela:</h4>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0.86em 0px 1.3em; padding: 0px; zoom: 1; font-size: 13px; letter-spacing: normal;\"><em style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; zoom: 1;\">a.)expoz&iacute;cia:</em>&nbsp;Ide o obozn&aacute;menie o živote Zuzany Čenkovej a jej 4 det&iacute; v minulosti a teraz.</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0.86em 0px 1.3em; padding: 0px; zoom: 1; font-size: 13px; letter-spacing: normal;\"><em style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; zoom: 1;\">b.)kol&iacute;zia:</em>&nbsp;Zuzana pred&aacute;va Paľka za 1000 Sk p&aacute;novi tov&aacute;rnikovi a jeho pani.</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0.86em 0px 1.3em; padding: 0px; zoom: 1; font-size: 13px; letter-spacing: normal;\"><em style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; zoom: 1;\">c.)kr&iacute;za:</em>&nbsp;Zuzana pred&aacute;va ďal&scaron;ie dve deti na trhu a zatkne ju policajt a deti si berie soci&aacute;lna starostlivosť.</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0.86em 0px 1.3em; padding: 0px; zoom: 1; font-size: 13px; letter-spacing: normal;\"><em style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; zoom: 1;\">d.)peripetia:</em>&nbsp;Mi&scaron;ko sa dost&aacute;va do rodiny obuvn&iacute;ka Kaspera a Hanka do rodiny gazdu Rigu na pustatine Bet&ouml;... Paľko žije v prepychu a hojnosti a Zuzana sa s Evičkou uchyľuje v služobnej hotelovej izbe.</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0.86em 0px 1.3em; padding: 0px; zoom: 1; font-size: 13px; letter-spacing: normal;\"><em style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; zoom: 1;\">e.)katastrofa:</em>&nbsp;V&scaron;etci sa op&auml;ť dost&aacute;vaj&uacute; k Mamičke ku jazierku.</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0.86em 0px 1.3em; padding: 0px; zoom: 1; font-size: 13px; letter-spacing: normal;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; zoom: 1;\">Horizont&aacute;lne členenie textu:</strong>&nbsp;dielo m&aacute; 5 hlavn&yacute;ch kapitol a 23 vedľaj&scaron;&iacute;ch ;123 str&aacute;n a jednotliv&eacute; kapitoly s&uacute; pomenovane n&aacute;zvami a s&uacute; rozdelen&eacute; na odseky</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0.86em 0px 1.3em; padding: 0px; zoom: 1; font-size: 13px; letter-spacing: normal;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; zoom: 1;\">Postavy</strong>:</p>\r\n<ul style=\"margin: 0.86em 0px 1.3em 1.3em; padding: 0px; zoom: 1; font-size: 13px; letter-spacing: normal;\">\r\n<li style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; zoom: 1;\">Zuzana Čenkov&aacute;;</li>\r\n<li style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; zoom: 1;\">Mi&scaron;o,</li>\r\n<li style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; zoom: 1;\">Hanka,</li>\r\n<li style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; zoom: 1;\">Paľko</li>\r\n<li style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; zoom: 1;\">Evička;</li>\r\n<li style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; zoom: 1;\">policajt,</li>\r\n<li style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; zoom: 1;\">opatrovateľky,</li>\r\n<li style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; zoom: 1;\">gazda Rigo,</li>\r\n<li style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; zoom: 1;\">Obuvn&iacute;k,</li>\r\n<li style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; zoom: 1;\">Kasper a jeho rodina,</li>\r\n<li style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; zoom: 1;\">učiteľ &Scaron;tefan Hronkin,</li>\r\n<li style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; zoom: 1;\">sprievodca,</li>\r\n<li style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; zoom: 1;\">d&ocirc;chodcovia,</li>\r\n<li style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; zoom: 1;\">chlapci</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h4 style=\"margin: 1.3em 0px 0px; padding: 0px; zoom: 1; font-weight: normal; line-height: 1.3em; font-size: 1.5em; color: #343131; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\">Obsah:</h4>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0.86em 0px 1.3em; padding: 0px; zoom: 1; font-size: 13px; letter-spacing: normal;\">OD MATKY DO SVETA<br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; zoom: 1;\" />T&aacute;to kapitola rozpr&aacute;va o tom, v akej biede žili pracuj&uacute;ci ľudia. Tak žila aj vdova Zuzana Čenkov&aacute; so svojimi deťmi pod horami Vysok&yacute;ch Tatier. Bl&iacute;ži se zima a matka se boj&iacute;, že cez zimu deti neuživ&iacute;. Preto pred&aacute; tov&aacute;rnikovi mal&eacute;ho Paľka. Za z&iacute;skan&eacute; peniaze k&uacute;pila oblečenie pre ostatn&eacute; deti a pre seba. Keď pri&scaron;la zima, nemali čo jesť. Matka se rozhodne, že pred&aacute; ďal&scaron;ie dve deti. Policajti na to pr&iacute;du a deti sa dostan&uacute; do &uacute;tulku pre ml&aacute;dež.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0.86em 0px 1.3em; padding: 0px; zoom: 1; font-size: 13px; letter-spacing: normal;\">MI&Scaron;O<br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; zoom: 1;\" />Dozved&aacute;me sa o živote Mi&scaron;a, ktor&yacute; bol dan&yacute; do soci&aacute;lnej starostlivosti do Bratislavy. Začal chodiť do &scaron;koly. Rodina obuvn&iacute;ka, u ktor&eacute;ho je Mi&scaron;o, dostane rakovinu pľ&uacute;c a Mi&scaron;o je tiež nakazen&yacute;. D&uacute;fa, že sa p&ocirc;jde liečiť do sanat&oacute;ria v Tatr&aacute;ch.</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0.86em 0px 1.3em; padding: 0px; zoom: 1; font-size: 13px; letter-spacing: normal;\">HANKA<br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; zoom: 1;\" />Hanka se dostala ku gazdovi Rigovi. Sp&aacute;vala v sene nad chlievom. Starala sa o kravy. Gazda a jeho rodina se nechovala k Hanke vľ&uacute;dne, a preto rozm&yacute;&scaron;ľala nad &uacute;tekom. Nesk&ocirc;r začala chodiť do &scaron;koly. Najviac ju zaj&iacute;mal zemepis. Dobre se orientovala na mape a pam&auml;tala si aj cestu domov. P&aacute;novi učiteľovi nosila mlieko a on jej za cestu d&aacute;val nejak&eacute; peniaze. Tak si pomaly &scaron;etrila. Raz dostala od Mi&scaron;a list a č&iacute;tala ho, keď dojila kravu. N&aacute;doba s mliekom jej vypadla a mlieko sa rozlialo. Hanka sa b&aacute;la, že ju hospod&aacute;r zbije, a utiekla domov.</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0.86em 0px 1.3em; padding: 0px; zoom: 1; font-size: 13px; letter-spacing: normal;\">PAĽKO<br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; zoom: 1;\" />Paľko žije v hojnosti a prepychu. Jeho panička, ktor&aacute; ho často tr&aacute;pi, ho vid&iacute; ako hračku. Jedn&eacute;ho dňa na ňu Paľko vyplazil jazyk a panička ho za to vyhodila. Aj Paľko se dostane domov. V piatej kapitole se nakoniec v&scaron;etci vr&aacute;tia do Tatier.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>'),
(25, 3, 3, 'Literatúra', '2024-01-24 15:36:29', 'ZŠ', '<p style=\"margin: 0.86em 0px 1.3em; padding: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #343131; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13px;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; zoom: 1;\">Literat&uacute;ra</strong>&nbsp;zahrňuje v&scaron;etky diela, ktor&eacute; použ&iacute;vaj&uacute; ako hlavn&uacute; formu prejavu jazyk.</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0.86em 0px 1.3em; padding: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #343131; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13px;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; zoom: 1;\">Literat&uacute;ra</strong>:</p>\r\n<ul style=\"margin: 0.86em 0px 1.3em 1.3em; padding: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #343131; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13px;\">\r\n<li style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; zoom: 1;\">vecn&aacute; - odborn&aacute;,</li>\r\n<li style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; zoom: 1;\">publicistick&aacute;,</li>\r\n<li style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; zoom: 1;\">administrat&iacute;vna,</li>\r\n<li style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; zoom: 1;\">stručn&aacute;</li>\r\n<li style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; zoom: 1;\">v&yacute;stižn&aacute;</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0.86em 0px 1.3em; padding: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #343131; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13px;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; zoom: 1;\">Umeleck&aacute;</strong>:kr&aacute;sna literat&uacute;ra, s&uacute; v nej liter&aacute;rne obrazy/ b&aacute;sne/</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0.86em 0px 1.3em; padding: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #343131; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13px;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; zoom: 1;\">Umel&aacute;</strong>: autor je zn&aacute;my.</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0.86em 0px 1.3em; padding: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #343131; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13px;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; zoom: 1;\">Ľudov&aacute;</strong>:: autor nieje zn&aacute;my.</p>\r\n<h4 style=\"margin: 1.3em 0px 0px; padding: 0px; zoom: 1; font-weight: normal; line-height: 1.3em; font-size: 1.5em; color: #343131; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\">Z&aacute;kladn&eacute; zložky liter&aacute;rneho diela /LD/</h4>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0.86em 0px 1.3em; padding: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #343131; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13px;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; zoom: 1;\">Obsah</strong>&nbsp;&ndash; tvor&iacute; ho t&eacute;ma a idea</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0.86em 0px 1.3em; padding: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #343131; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13px;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; zoom: 1;\">T&eacute;ma</strong>&nbsp;&ndash; s&uacute; to r&ocirc;zne udalosti a fakty o ktor&yacute;ch autor hovor&iacute;.</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0.86em 0px 1.3em; padding: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #343131; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13px;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; zoom: 1;\">Idea</strong>&nbsp;&ndash; z&aacute;kladn&aacute; my&scaron;lienka LD</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0.86em 0px 1.3em; padding: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #343131; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13px;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; zoom: 1;\">Forma</strong>&nbsp;&ndash; je to sp&ocirc;sob ak&yacute;m autor obsah realizuje</p>\r\n<h4 style=\"margin: 1.3em 0px 0px; padding: 0px; zoom: 1; font-weight: normal; line-height: 1.3em; font-size: 1.5em; color: #343131; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\">Sp&ocirc;sob zobrazovania skutočnosti v LD</h4>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0.86em 0px 1.3em; padding: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #343131; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13px;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; zoom: 1;\">Epick&eacute; rozpr&aacute;vanie</strong>&nbsp;- je to rozv&iacute;janie deja v čase</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0.86em 0px 1.3em; padding: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #343131; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13px;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; zoom: 1;\">Opis</strong>&nbsp;- autor ho využ&iacute;va na zobrazovanie prostredia v ktorom sa dej odohr&aacute;va.</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0.86em 0px 1.3em; padding: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #343131; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13px;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; zoom: 1;\">Charakteristika</strong>&nbsp;- Autor v ňom vystihuje vlastnosti postavy</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0.86em 0px 1.3em; padding: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #343131; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13px;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; zoom: 1;\">Priama</strong>&nbsp;- autor priamo vymen&uacute;va vlastnosti postavy</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0.86em 0px 1.3em; padding: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #343131; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13px;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; zoom: 1;\">Nepriama</strong>&nbsp;- b&yacute;va vyjadren&aacute; konan&iacute;m alebo rečou.</p>\r\n<h4 style=\"margin: 1.3em 0px 0px; padding: 0px; zoom: 1; font-weight: normal; line-height: 1.3em; font-size: 1.5em; color: #343131; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\">Umeleck&eacute; jazykov&eacute; prostriedky</h4>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0.86em 0px 1.3em; padding: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #343131; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13px;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; zoom: 1;\">zdrobneniny</strong>&nbsp;- pr&iacute;značn&eacute; pre ľudov&uacute; slovesnosť. S&uacute; to zjemňuj&uacute;ce slov&aacute;, použ&iacute;vaj&uacute; sa na vyjadrenie citov&eacute;ho vzťahu.</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0.86em 0px 1.3em; padding: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #343131; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13px;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; zoom: 1;\">Epiteton&nbsp;</strong>- b&aacute;snick&yacute; pr&iacute;vlastok /zd&ocirc;raznenie niektorej vlastnosti/ - zlat&eacute; nite, modrast&eacute; oči p&yacute;tame sa naň ot&aacute;zkami: ak&yacute;, ak&aacute;, ak&eacute;.</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0.86em 0px 1.3em; padding: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #343131; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13px;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; zoom: 1;\">Metafora</strong>&nbsp;- obrazn&eacute; pomenovanie na z&aacute;klade vonkaj&scaron;&iacute;ch podobnost&iacute;./ hust&yacute; d&aacute;žď/</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0.86em 0px 1.3em; padding: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #343131; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13px;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; zoom: 1;\">metonymia&nbsp;</strong>- pren&aacute;&scaron;anie v&yacute;znamu na z&aacute;klade vn&uacute;torn&yacute;ch podobnost&iacute;. Je to druh metafory.</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0.86em 0px 1.3em; padding: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #343131; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13px;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; zoom: 1;\">Personifik&aacute;cia</strong>- zosobnenie- neživ&yacute;m predmetom sa pripisuj&uacute; ľudsk&eacute; vlastnosti. /Mesiac sa d&iacute;va/</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0.86em 0px 1.3em; padding: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #343131; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13px;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; zoom: 1;\">B&aacute;snick&aacute; rečn&iacute;cka ot&aacute;zka</strong>&nbsp;- na ktor&uacute; si b&aacute;snik d&aacute;va odpoveď priamo alebo nepriamo.</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0.86em 0px 1.3em; padding: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #343131; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13px;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; zoom: 1;\">Prirovnanie</strong>&nbsp;- porovnanie dvoch javov s cieľom dosiahnuť lep&scaron;iu n&aacute;zornosť alebo niečo zv&yacute;razniť. /siln&yacute; ako buk, rovn&yacute; ako st&ocirc;l/.</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0.86em 0px 1.3em; padding: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #343131; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13px;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; zoom: 1;\">Anafora</strong>&nbsp;- opakovanie slov na začiatku ver&scaron;ov.</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0.86em 0px 1.3em; padding: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #343131; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13px;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; zoom: 1;\">Epifora&nbsp;</strong>- opakovanie slov na konci ver&scaron;ov.</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0.86em 0px 1.3em; padding: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #343131; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13px;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; zoom: 1;\">Epanastrofa&nbsp;</strong>- opakovanie slov na začiatku a konci ver&scaron;ov.</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0.86em 0px 1.3em; padding: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #343131; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13px;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; zoom: 1;\">Refr&eacute;n</strong>&nbsp;- opakovanie jedn&eacute;ho alebo viacer&yacute;ch ver&scaron;ov či in&yacute;ch &uacute;sekov textu na konci strof a odsekov. Zd&ocirc;razňuje niektor&uacute; my&scaron;lienku.</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0.86em 0px 1.3em; padding: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #343131; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13px;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; zoom: 1;\">Aleg&oacute;ria</strong>&nbsp;- utajen&yacute; zmysel</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0.86em 0px 1.3em; padding: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #343131; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13px;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; zoom: 1;\">Aliter&aacute;cia&nbsp;</strong>- opakovanie rovnak&yacute;ch alebo zvukovo podobn&yacute;ch hl&aacute;sok.</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0.86em 0px 1.3em; padding: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #343131; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13px;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; zoom: 1;\">Biologick&yacute; rom&aacute;n</strong>&nbsp;- autor v ňom vych&aacute;dza zo životopisn&yacute;ch prameňov.</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0.86em 0px 1.3em; padding: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #343131; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13px;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; zoom: 1;\">Bylina</strong>&nbsp;- rusk&aacute; n&aacute;rodn&aacute; povesť</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0.86em 0px 1.3em; padding: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #343131; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13px;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; zoom: 1;\">Dej</strong>&nbsp;- hlavn&yacute; znak epick&eacute;ho diela</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0.86em 0px 1.3em; padding: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #343131; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13px;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; zoom: 1;\">Dialektika</strong>&nbsp;- s&uacute; to miestne slov&aacute;</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0.86em 0px 1.3em; padding: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #343131; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13px;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; zoom: 1;\">Epizeuxa</strong>&nbsp;- opakovanie slov alebo skupiny slov za sebou.</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0.86em 0px 1.3em; padding: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #343131; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13px;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; zoom: 1;\">Fig&uacute;ry</strong>&nbsp;- umeleck&eacute; alebo jazykov&eacute; prostriedky</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0.86em 0px 1.3em; padding: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #343131; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13px;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; zoom: 1;\">Grad&aacute;cia</strong>&nbsp;- stupňovanie</p>\r\n<h4 style=\"margin: 1.3em 0px 0px; padding: 0px; zoom: 1; font-weight: normal; line-height: 1.3em; font-size: 1.5em; color: #343131; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\">Liter&aacute;rne druhy</h4>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0.86em 0px 1.3em; padding: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #343131; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13px;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; zoom: 1;\">Epika</strong>&nbsp;&ndash; z&aacute;kladn&yacute;m znakom je rozpr&aacute;vanie a opis udalost&iacute;. Epick&eacute; diela m&ocirc;žu byť ver&scaron;ovan&eacute; alebo prozaick&eacute;. Do epiky patr&iacute; predov&scaron;etk&yacute;m:</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0.86em 0px 1.3em; padding: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #343131; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13px;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; zoom: 1;\">Epos</strong>&nbsp;- rozsiahla b&aacute;seň</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0.86em 0px 1.3em; padding: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #343131; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13px;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; zoom: 1;\">Balada</strong>&nbsp;- b&aacute;seň stredn&eacute;ho až krat&scaron;ieho rozsahu s pochm&uacute;rnym dejom a tragick&yacute;m koncom.</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0.86em 0px 1.3em; padding: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #343131; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13px;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; zoom: 1;\">B&aacute;jka</strong>&nbsp;- kr&aacute;tka epick&aacute; forma</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0.86em 0px 1.3em; padding: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #343131; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13px;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; zoom: 1;\">B&aacute;j</strong>&nbsp;- m&yacute;tus; zachyt&aacute;va predstavy ľud&iacute; d&aacute;vnych d&ocirc;b o svete, o pr&iacute;rode, o živote človeka a Bohov. S&uacute;hrn b&aacute;j&iacute; ist&eacute;ho n&aacute;roda sa naz&yacute;va &ndash; b&aacute;joslovie/ mytol&oacute;gia.</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0.86em 0px 1.3em; padding: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #343131; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13px;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; zoom: 1;\">Rozpr&aacute;vka</strong>&nbsp;- typick&yacute; prejav ľudovej slovesnosti. Vymyslen&yacute; pr&iacute;beh sa neviaže na konkr&eacute;tny priestor a čas.</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0.86em 0px 1.3em; padding: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #343131; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13px;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; zoom: 1;\">Povesť</strong>&nbsp;- popri rozpr&aacute;vke najroz&scaron;&iacute;renej&scaron;&iacute; &uacute;tvar ľudovej slovesnosti. Jej dej, miesto deja, postavy s&uacute; historicky konkr&eacute;tnej&scaron;ie ako v rozpr&aacute;vke. Obsahuje veľa vymyslen&yacute;ch prvkov.</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0.86em 0px 1.3em; padding: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #343131; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13px;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; zoom: 1;\">Poviedka</strong>&nbsp;- kr&aacute;tka epick&aacute; forma s jednoduch&yacute;m dejom a men&scaron;&iacute;m počtom post&aacute;v.</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0.86em 0px 1.3em; padding: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #343131; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13px;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; zoom: 1;\">Novela&nbsp;</strong>- n&aacute;ročnej&scaron;&iacute; &uacute;tvar ako poviedka. Z&aacute;kladom je jeden dramatick&yacute; pr&iacute;beh bez opisov a epiz&oacute;d, konč&iacute; sa v&yacute;razn&yacute;m často prekvapuj&uacute;cim koncom.</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0.86em 0px 1.3em; padding: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #343131; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13px;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; zoom: 1;\">Rom&aacute;n&nbsp;</strong>- najrozsiahlej&scaron;ia epick&aacute; forma. Zobrazuje udalosti a osudy post&aacute;v v r&ocirc;znych prostrediach.</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0.86em 0px 1.3em; padding: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #343131; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13px;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0.86em 0px 1.3em; padding: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #343131; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13px;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; zoom: 1;\">Lyrika</strong>&nbsp;- Vyjadruje osobn&eacute;, subjekt&iacute;vne my&scaron;lienky, pocity alebo n&aacute;lady autora. Lyrick&eacute; diela s&uacute; najčastej&scaron;ie ver&scaron;ovan&eacute;. Podľa obsahu rozdeľujeme lyriku na osobn&uacute;, pr&iacute;rodn&uacute; a spoločensk&uacute;. Do lyriky patria predov&scaron;etk&yacute;m.:</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0.86em 0px 1.3em; padding: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #343131; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13px;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; zoom: 1;\">&Oacute;da</strong>&nbsp;&ndash; chv&aacute;lospev- b&aacute;seň oslavuj&uacute;ca v&yacute;znamn&uacute; udalosť, osobnosť, vlasť, my&scaron;lienku.</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0.86em 0px 1.3em; padding: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #343131; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13px;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; zoom: 1;\">El&eacute;gia</strong>&nbsp;- žalospev- b&aacute;seň vyjadruj&uacute;ca žiaľ nad stratou drahej bytosti alebo veci.</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0.86em 0px 1.3em; padding: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #343131; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13px;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; zoom: 1;\">Hymna</strong>&nbsp;- sl&aacute;vnostn&aacute; b&aacute;seň, ospevuj&uacute;ca vzne&scaron;en&uacute; my&scaron;lienku, ktor&aacute; sp&aacute;ja nejak&yacute; kolekt&iacute;v. Osobitn&yacute;m druhom je &scaron;t&aacute;tna hymna.</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0.86em 0px 1.3em; padding: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #343131; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13px;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; zoom: 1;\">Epigram</strong>&nbsp;- krat&scaron;ia vtipn&aacute; b&aacute;seň s v&yacute;raznou pointou. Zosmie&scaron;ňuje nejak&uacute; negat&iacute;vnu vlastnosť.</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0.86em 0px 1.3em; padding: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #343131; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13px;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; zoom: 1;\">Aforizmus</strong>&nbsp;- stručn&aacute;, v&yacute;stižn&aacute; v&yacute;poveď, obsahuj&uacute;ca vtipn&uacute; my&scaron;lienku, postreh. Je bl&iacute;zky porekadlu.</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0.86em 0px 1.3em; padding: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #343131; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13px;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0.86em 0px 1.3em; padding: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #343131; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13px;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; zoom: 1;\">Dramatick&eacute; diela</strong>- /divadeln&eacute; hry/- podobne ako epick&eacute; diela s&uacute; založen&eacute; na deji. Z&aacute;kladn&eacute; dramatick&eacute; ž&aacute;nre s&uacute; kom&eacute;dia, trag&eacute;dia, činohra.</p>');
INSERT INTO `referaty` (`referat_id`, `user_id`, `category_id`, `title`, `created_at`, `skola`, `content`) VALUES
(26, 3, 3, 'Barok', '2024-01-24 15:37:00', 'ZŠ', '<h4 style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; zoom: 1; font-weight: normal; line-height: 1.3em; font-size: 1.5em; color: #343131; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\">Barok</h4>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0.86em 0px 1.3em; padding: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #343131; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13px;\">Barok, umeleck&yacute; sloh. Vznikol v Taliansku na konci 16. storočia. Odtiaľ sa pomerne r&yacute;chlo roz&scaron;&iacute;ril do ostatn&yacute;ch kraj&iacute;n Eur&oacute;py a pretrval až do konca 18 storočia. Svojou formou nadv&auml;zuje na Manirizmus a Renesanciu. Hlavn&yacute;m zmyslom baroka je vyjadrenie božskej i svetskej n&aacute;dhery, sily a moci, v urbanistickom meradle potom absol&uacute;tne zaujatie krajiny. Nato využ&iacute;va grandi&oacute;zne urbanistick&eacute; kompoz&iacute;cie -&nbsp; dlh&eacute; osi a priehľady, zv&auml;č&scaron;enie mierky tektonick&yacute;ch čl&aacute;nkov budov a ich zmnožovanie, i cieľavedom&eacute; perspekt&iacute;vne klamy.<br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; zoom: 1;\" /><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; zoom: 1;\" />Prvky klasickej architekt&uacute;ry slobodne deformuje a pozmeňuje ( napr. stĺpy so &scaron;pir&aacute;lov&yacute;mi driekmi, rozoklan&eacute; frontony a i. ). Geometria stavieb v sebe často skr&yacute;va symbolick&eacute; a alegorick&eacute; v&yacute;znamy. Od začiatku sa daj&uacute; rozl&iacute;&scaron;it dva pr&uacute;dy v&yacute;voja baroka-klasicizuj&uacute;ci, ktor&yacute; sa drž&iacute; renesančn&yacute;ch a manieristick&yacute;ch vzorov a radik&aacute;lny(dynamick&yacute;), ktor&yacute; voľne zaobch&aacute;dza so v&scaron;etk&yacute;mi prostriedkami architektonickej&nbsp;tvorby. Ten je vyjadren&iacute;m vystupňovan&eacute;ho citov&eacute;ho vzťahu barokov&eacute;ho človeka k Bohu a k svetu. Vytv&aacute;ra zložit&eacute; kon&scaron;trukcie navz&aacute;jom sa prel&iacute;naj&uacute;cich priestorov, deformuje a zvlňuje m&uacute;ry aj klasick&eacute; tektonick&eacute; čl&aacute;nky.<br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; zoom: 1;\" /><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; zoom: 1;\" />Často využ&iacute;va iluz&iacute;vne maľby. Vyvol&aacute;va dojem pohybu priestoru aj hmoty. V&nbsp;Taliansku boli jeho hlavn&yacute;mi reprezentantmi G.Bernini, F.Borromini či G.Guarnini. Franc&uacute;zsko sa prikl&aacute;ňa ku klasicizuj&uacute;cemu smeru baroka; typick&yacute;m pr&iacute;kladom je prevažn&aacute; časť kr&aacute;ľovsk&eacute;ho z&aacute;mku vo Versailles. Podobn&eacute; je to v Anglicku, kde je ved&uacute;cou postavou C. Wren.<br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; zoom: 1;\" /><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; zoom: 1;\" />V hudbe tento term&iacute;n označuje zložit&uacute; a ornament&aacute;lnu hudbu skladateľov v obdob&iacute; rokov 1600-1750. Medzi barokov&yacute;ch skladateľov patr&iacute; Monteverdi, Purcell, Vivaldi, Bach a H&auml;ndel.&nbsp;&nbsp;</p>'),
(27, 3, 3, 'Matúš Kučera - Konštantín a Metod', '2024-01-24 15:37:13', 'ZŠ', '<p style=\"margin: 0.86em 0px 1.3em; padding: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #343131; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13px;\">Kon&scaron;tant&iacute;n a&nbsp;Metod sa narodili v&nbsp;gr&eacute;ckom meste Thessalonike. Slovanom sa tento n&aacute;zov zdal pridlh&yacute; a&nbsp;preto z&nbsp;neho zobrali iba jednu časť Salon&eacute;, z čoho potom vznikol n&aacute;zov Sol&uacute;n. Rozkladal sa na pobrež&iacute; Egejsk&eacute;ho mora. Od konca 6.stročia uskutočnili Slovania vojensk&eacute; &uacute;toky na mesto. Obsadili tak kraje Sol&uacute;na a&nbsp;postupne prenikli aj do vn&uacute;tra mesta. Keď tu žili Kon&scaron;tant&iacute;n a&nbsp;Metod, b&yacute;valo tu najviac Gr&eacute;kov a&nbsp;Slovanov a&nbsp;okrem nich aj veľa etnick&yacute;ch skup&iacute;n. Kon&scaron;tant&iacute;n a&nbsp;Metod mali otca-Lev a&nbsp;mamu-M&aacute;ria. Obaja chlapci vedeli sloviensky jazyk, hovorili n&iacute;m. A&nbsp;preto ich Michal III. poslal na Veľk&uacute; Moravu. Niektor&iacute; s&uacute;dili, že ich otec bol slovan, a&nbsp;keď nie otec tak mama, ktor&aacute; ich učila slovienčinu. Už od detstva boli bilingvisti. Poch&aacute;dzali vraj zo siedmych det&iacute; aj keď sa o&nbsp;ďal&scaron;&iacute;ch s&uacute;rodencoch nič nevie.&nbsp;Kon&scaron;tant&iacute;n bol z&nbsp;nich najmlad&scaron;&iacute;, narodil sa v&nbsp;roku 836. Metod bol od neho stra&scaron;&iacute; o&nbsp;10 rokov. Vzdelanie z&iacute;skali v&nbsp;sol&uacute;nskych &scaron;kol&aacute;ch. Keď mal Kon&scaron;tant&iacute;n 14 rokov, zomrel mu otec. Mama mala preto obavy, že svojmu najtalentovanej&scaron;iemu synovi nebude m&ocirc;cť dopriať vy&scaron;&scaron;ie vzdelanie. Jeho otec mal dobr&eacute;ho priateľa na cis&aacute;rskom dvore. Ten sa postaral o&nbsp;chlapca a&nbsp;zap&iacute;sal ho na najlep&scaron;iu &scaron;kolu na cis&aacute;rskom dvore, na ktorej nesk&ocirc;r &scaron;tudoval aj Michal III. Metod bol praktickej&scaron;&iacute; človek. Vzorom mu bol otec. &Scaron;tudoval pr&aacute;vo, a&nbsp;nesk&ocirc;r sa stal spr&aacute;vcom župy, učiteľom a&nbsp;arcibiskupom Slovanov.</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0.86em 0px 1.3em; padding: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #343131; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13px;\">&nbsp;</p>'),
(28, 3, 3, 'Príhovor', '2024-01-24 15:37:26', 'ZŠ', '<p style=\"margin: 0.86em 0px 1.3em; padding: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #343131; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13px;\">V&aacute;žen&aacute; pani učiteľka, mil&iacute; spolužiaci!</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0.86em 0px 1.3em; padding: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #343131; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13px;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0.86em 0px 1.3em; padding: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #343131; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13px;\">Dovoľte, aby som V&aacute;s poinformovala o &scaron;kolskom roku dne&scaron;n&yacute;ch &scaron;k&ocirc;l. Konkr&eacute;tne ide o Z&aacute;kladn&uacute; &scaron;kolu vo Veľk&yacute;ch Kostoľanoch.</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0.86em 0px 1.3em; padding: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #343131; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13px;\">Na začiatku &scaron;kolsk&eacute;ho roku žiakov a cel&yacute; učiteľsk&yacute; zbor priv&iacute;ta riaditeľ &scaron;koly. Po pr&iacute;hovore riaditeľa je pripraven&eacute; mal&eacute; predstavenie, ktor&eacute; vytvorili sami žiaci v spolupr&aacute;ci s učiteľmi. S&uacute; to sc&eacute;nky z r&ocirc;znych seri&aacute;lov alebo filmov. Po tomto predstaven&iacute; sa sl&aacute;vnostne otvor&iacute; nov&yacute; &scaron;kolsk&yacute; rok. Žiaci sa odober&uacute; do svojich tried kde ich priv&iacute;ta triedny učiteľ. Cel&yacute; deň s&uacute; so svojim učiteľom preberaj&uacute; z&aacute;žitky s pr&aacute;zdnin a hraj&uacute; r&ocirc;zne hry. Pri konci dňa im triedny učiteľ povie pokyny na nasleduj&uacute;ci &scaron;kolsk&yacute; rok a d&aacute; im rozvrh hod&iacute;n. Od ďal&scaron;ieho dňa sa začne vyučovanie. Zozn&aacute;mia sa s nov&yacute;mi učiteľmi niektor&iacute; aj s nov&yacute;mi predmetmi. Uplynie mesiac, dva a s&uacute; tu jesenn&eacute; pr&aacute;zdniny.</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0.86em 0px 1.3em; padding: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #343131; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13px;\">Po pr&aacute;zdnin&aacute;ch je cel&aacute; atmosf&eacute;ra tak&aacute; sviatočn&aacute;- vianočn&aacute;. V&scaron;etci hovoria o z&aacute;žitkoch z predch&aacute;dzaj&uacute;cich Vianoc a te&scaron;ia sa na nasleduj&uacute;ce. Deň pred vianočn&yacute;mi pr&aacute;zdninami každ&yacute; žiak k&uacute;pi mal&yacute; darček podľa vlastn&eacute;ho uv&aacute;ženia. Učiteľ vhod&iacute; do misky papieriky s menami v&scaron;etk&yacute;ch žiakov. Každ&yacute; žiak si vytiahne jeden l&iacute;stoček a tomu koho meno je na ňom nap&iacute;san&eacute; d&aacute; svoj darček. Nakoniec daj&uacute; jeden spoločn&yacute; darček svojmu triednemu učiteľovi. Potom sa v&scaron;etci rozl&uacute;čia a id&uacute; domov oslavovať Vianoce. Po takmer dvoch t&yacute;ždňoch sa žiaci vr&aacute;tia do &scaron;koly a zasadn&uacute; do lav&iacute;c. Začn&uacute; sa učiť hneď na druh&yacute; deň, lebo ten prv&yacute; je venovan&yacute; Vianociam. Rozpr&aacute;vaj&uacute; sa spolu s učiteľmi o Vianociach, čo dostali pod stromček a podobne. Keď sa rozpust&iacute; sneh, začn&uacute; tr&eacute;novať na &scaron;kolsk&yacute;ch kurtoch tenis. Keď s&uacute; vybran&yacute; žiaci dostatočne pripraven&yacute;, ide sa na s&uacute;ťaž. Po niekoľk&yacute;ch turnajoch prich&aacute;dza zasl&uacute;žen&yacute; odpočinok v podobe jarn&yacute;ch pr&aacute;zdnin. Potom sa už len učia, opravuj&uacute; zn&aacute;mky, čakaj&uacute; na vysvedčenie a na vyt&uacute;žen&eacute; letn&eacute; pr&aacute;zdniny. Pred koncom &scaron;kolsk&eacute;ho roku maj&uacute; rozl&uacute;čenie s uplynul&yacute;m rokom a z vych&aacute;dzaj&uacute;cimi žiakmi deviateho ročn&iacute;ka. V posledn&yacute; deň &scaron;kolsk&eacute;ho roku maj&uacute; tak ako na začiatku mal&eacute; predstavenie najmen&scaron;&iacute;ch prv&aacute;čikov a pr&iacute;hovor riaditeľa &scaron;koly. Riaditeľ sa s nimi rozl&uacute;či a žiaci odch&aacute;dzaj&uacute; spolu s triednym učiteľom do triedy. Tam im učiteľ povie p&aacute;r slov a rozd&aacute; vysvedčenia. Keď už maj&uacute; v&scaron;etci žiaci vysvedčenie v ruk&aacute;ch, zost&aacute;va už len p&aacute;r min&uacute;t do zatvorenia &scaron;kolskej br&aacute;ny. Tie str&aacute;via s triednym učiteľom vo svojej triede. Rozl&uacute;čia sa medzi sebou i s učiteľom.</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0.86em 0px 1.3em; padding: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #343131; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13px;\">A takto sa skonč&iacute; &scaron;kolsk&yacute; rok a žiaci utekaj&uacute; domov pochv&aacute;liť sa so svojimi v&yacute;sledkami celoročn&eacute;ho &uacute;silia. Zač&iacute;naj&uacute; sa dlho očak&aacute;van&eacute; letn&eacute; dvojmesačn&eacute; pr&aacute;zdniny. D&uacute;fam, že ďal&scaron;&iacute; rok bude rovnako &uacute;spe&scaron;n&yacute; možno aj viac ako ten minul&yacute;.</p>'),
(29, 3, 3, 'Josef Kajetan Tyl: Strakonický dudák', '2024-01-24 15:37:46', 'ZŠ', '<p style=\"margin: 0.86em 0px 1.3em; padding: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #343131; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13px;\">Tato hra je vrcholem Tylovy divadeln&iacute; tvorby. Tyl v n&iacute; zn&aacute;zorňuje l&aacute;sku k rodn&eacute; zemi a protestuje proti touze po cizině. Prol&iacute;n&aacute; se zde opravdov&yacute; život s poh&aacute;dkov&yacute;mi prvky.</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0.86em 0px 1.3em; padding: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #343131; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13px;\">Hlavn&iacute; postavou je zde &Scaron;vanda, dud&aacute;k, chud&yacute; chlapec, kter&yacute; žije v malebn&eacute; jihočesk&eacute; vesničce. &Scaron;vanda m&aacute; r&aacute;d svou milou, Dorotku, dceru hajn&eacute;ho, kter&yacute; v&scaron;ak jejich l&aacute;sce nepřeje, protože &Scaron;vanda je chud&yacute; prost&yacute; chlapec. O posv&iacute;cen&iacute; se &Scaron;vanda dověděl od voj&aacute;ka &Scaron;avličky, že ve světě lze snadno zbohatnout. Proto se s Dorotkou rozloučil a &scaron;el do světa. Při jeho pouti ho ochraňuje jeho matka Rosava, kter&aacute; pros&iacute; lesn&iacute; panny, aby mu do dud daly kr&aacute;su sv&yacute;ch p&iacute;sn&iacute;. Tak byla &Scaron;vandov&yacute;m dudům d&aacute;na z&aacute;zračn&aacute; moc.</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0.86em 0px 1.3em; padding: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #343131; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13px;\">&Scaron;vanda přich&aacute;z&iacute; do bohat&eacute; země Tureck&eacute;, kde potk&aacute;v&aacute; podvodn&iacute;ka Vocilku, kter&yacute; využ&iacute;v&aacute; jeho důvěry. &Scaron;vandovi se podařilo pomoc&iacute; sv&yacute;ch dud rozesm&aacute;t princeznu Zuliku a je bohatě odměněn. Zulika se m&aacute; st&aacute;t jeho ženou. &Scaron;vanda zapom&iacute;n&aacute; na Dorotku a domov a je jako om&aacute;men&yacute;. Je uvězněn do vězen&iacute; princeznin&yacute;m n&aacute;padn&iacute;kem. Zaat&iacute;m Dorotka se doma tr&aacute;p&iacute;, a protože j&iacute; zemřel otec, rozhodla se vydat za sv&yacute;m mil&yacute;m.</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0.86em 0px 1.3em; padding: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #343131; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13px;\">Přemluv&iacute; sv&eacute;ho př&iacute;tele houslistu Kalafunu a oba odch&aacute;zej&iacute; hledat &Scaron;vandu. Teprve ve vězen&iacute; si &Scaron;vanda uvědomil svou chybu. Pomůže mu jeho matka, kter&aacute; mu v&scaron;echno řekne a chce ho osvobodit. Av&scaron;ak Lesana, kr&aacute;lovna v&iacute;l, ji uvrhne mezi div&eacute; ženy. &Scaron;vanda sepomoc&iacute; kouzeln&yacute;ch dud a vern&eacute; l&aacute;sky Dorotky dost&aacute;v&aacute; na svobodu a vrac&iacute; se domů. Opět se setk&aacute;v&aacute; s Vocilkou, kter&yacute; l&aacute;k&aacute; &Scaron;vandu o půlnoci do lesa, a chce mu ukr&aacute;st kouzeln&eacute; dudy.</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0.86em 0px 1.3em; padding: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #343131; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13px;\">Av&scaron;ak divoženky Vocilku odl&aacute;kaj&iacute; a &Scaron;vanda mus&iacute; hr&aacute;t na divok&eacute;m reji divoženek, kter&eacute; ho chtěj&iacute; zahubit. Ale věrn&aacute; l&aacute;ska Dorotčina vysvobod&iacute; &Scaron;vandu z moci kouzel. &Scaron;vanda odhod&iacute; sv&eacute; dudy, kter&eacute; t&iacute;m ztr&aacute;cej&iacute; svou kouzelnou moc. Společně s Dorotkou pak odch&aacute;z&iacute; do rodn&eacute; vsi, kde &scaron;ťastně obhospodařuj&iacute; h&aacute;jovnu po otci. Tak&eacute; kr&aacute;lovna odpou&scaron;t&iacute; Rosaně, protože ch&aacute;pe jej&iacute; l&aacute;sku k vlastn&iacute;mu d&iacute;těti a opět ji přij&iacute;m&aacute; ve sv&eacute; ř&iacute;&scaron;i.</p>'),
(31, 25, 5, 'Etika v podnikaní', '2024-01-24 15:39:05', 'VŠ', '<p style=\"margin: 0.86em 0px 1.3em; padding: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #343131; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13px;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; zoom: 1;\">Etika</strong></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0.86em 0px 1.3em; padding: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #343131; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13px;\"><em style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; zoom: 1;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; zoom: 1;\">Slovo etika poch&aacute;dza z&nbsp;gr&eacute;ckeho slova ethos, toto slovo m&ocirc;žeme vysvetliť dvojak&yacute;m sp&ocirc;sobom:</strong></em></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0.86em 0px 1.3em; padding: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #343131; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13px;\">1.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Spoločensk&eacute; pravidl&aacute; ľud&iacute; t&yacute;kaj&uacute;ce sa spr&aacute;vania.</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0.86em 0px 1.3em; padding: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #343131; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13px;\">2.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Charakter konkr&eacute;tneho človeka, jeho zvyky, trad&iacute;cie, mor&aacute;lka, n&aacute;vyky.</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0.86em 0px 1.3em; padding: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #343131; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13px;\">Slovo&nbsp;<strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; zoom: 1;\">mor&aacute;lka</strong>&nbsp;poch&aacute;dza z&nbsp;latinsk&eacute;ho slova m&oacute;res, čo znamen&aacute; zvyk, obyčaj, charakter, vlastnosť.</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0.86em 0px 1.3em; padding: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #343131; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13px;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; zoom: 1;\">Etika</strong>&nbsp;je vedn&aacute; discipl&iacute;na, ktor&aacute; sk&uacute;ma ako sa človek spr&aacute;va pri v&yacute;bere z&nbsp;minim&aacute;lne dvoch možnosti konania v&nbsp;danej situ&aacute;cii.</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0.86em 0px 1.3em; padding: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #343131; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13px;\">Etiku by sme mohli definovať aj ako vedu o&nbsp;spr&aacute;van&iacute;.</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0.86em 0px 1.3em; padding: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #343131; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13px;\">Hodnoty vych&aacute;dzaj&uacute; zo z&aacute;kladn&yacute;ch z&aacute;ujmov jednotlivca ale aj celej spoločnosti. Každ&yacute; človek m&aacute; in&yacute; rebr&iacute;ček hodn&ocirc;t.</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0.86em 0px 1.3em; padding: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #343131; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13px;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; zoom: 1;\">Etick&eacute; princ&iacute;py</strong>&nbsp;s&uacute; s&uacute;bor zvykov a&nbsp;nep&iacute;san&yacute;ch pravidiel, ktor&eacute; ľudia považuj&uacute; za svoje hodnoty. Etick&eacute; princ&iacute;py v&nbsp;r&ocirc;znych k&uacute;toch sveta sa l&iacute;&scaron;ia.</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0.86em 0px 1.3em; padding: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #343131; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13px;\">To znamen&aacute; to čo my považujeme za dobr&eacute;, tak ľudia v&nbsp;Iraku nemusia považovať za dobr&eacute;.</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0.86em 0px 1.3em; padding: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #343131; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13px;\">My považujeme bozk&aacute;vanie žien na verejnosti za etick&eacute;, ale ľudia v&nbsp;Iraku to považuj&uacute; za neetick&eacute;.</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0.86em 0px 1.3em; padding: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #343131; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13px;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; zoom: 1;\">Etapy v&yacute;voja etiky v&nbsp;podnikan&iacute;:</strong></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0.86em 0px 1.3em; padding: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #343131; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13px;\">1. Etapa (1900-1920) - proces hľadania etiky v&nbsp;podnikan&iacute; - v&nbsp;tejto etape&nbsp; hľadali sa možnosti zaradenia etiky do podnikania</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0.86em 0px 1.3em; padding: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #343131; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13px;\">2. Etapa (1921-1950) - proces snahy uznania etiky podnikania ako profesie - v&nbsp;tejto etape bola&nbsp; snaha o&nbsp;vytvorenie profesie, v&nbsp;ktorej bud&uacute; zamestnanci, ktor&iacute; sa bud&uacute; vyznať etike v&nbsp;podniku &nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0.86em 0px 1.3em; padding: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #343131; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13px;\">3. Etapa&nbsp; (1951-1970) - proces narastania komplexnosti etiky podnikania</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0.86em 0px 1.3em; padding: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #343131; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13px;\">4. Etapa (1971- s&uacute;časnosť) - etika podnikania sa st&aacute;va samostatnou vednou discipl&iacute;nou - etika v podnikan&iacute; v&nbsp;tejto etape sa stala predmetom z&aacute;ujmu vedy</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0.86em 0px 1.3em; padding: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #343131; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13px;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0.86em 0px 1.3em; padding: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #343131; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13px;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; zoom: 1;\">Defin&iacute;cia etick&eacute;ho k&oacute;dexu:</strong></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0.86em 0px 1.3em; padding: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #343131; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13px;\"><em style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; zoom: 1;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; zoom: 1;\">Etick&yacute; k&oacute;dex</strong></em>&nbsp;je listina, ktor&aacute; určuje čo považuje podnik z&nbsp;hľadiska spr&aacute;vania sa&nbsp; zamestnancov za etick&eacute;. V&nbsp;jednom podniku sa určit&eacute; konanie m&ocirc;že považovať za etick&eacute; a&nbsp;v&nbsp;druhom už nie.</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0.86em 0px 1.3em; padding: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #343131; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13px;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; zoom: 1;\">Ciele etick&eacute;ho k&oacute;dexu:</strong></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0.86em 0px 1.3em; padding: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #343131; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13px;\">1.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Cieľ vyh&yacute;bania sa neetick&eacute;ho spr&aacute;vania sa zamestnancov, ktor&eacute; je v&nbsp;nes&uacute;lade s&nbsp;pracovnou discipl&iacute;nou.&nbsp;&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0.86em 0px 1.3em; padding: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #343131; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13px;\">2.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Pomoc pri n&aacute;vrhoch disciplin&aacute;rneho konania pri poru&scaron;en&iacute; etick&eacute;ho spr&aacute;vania sa zamestnancov v&nbsp;danej firme - etick&yacute; k&oacute;dex pom&aacute;ha pri určen&iacute; trestu pre zamestnanca pri poru&scaron;en&iacute; pracovnej discipl&iacute;ny.</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0.86em 0px 1.3em; padding: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #343131; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13px;\">3.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Pomoc pri rie&scaron;en&iacute;&nbsp; dilem &nbsp;spr&aacute;vania sa zamestnancov v&nbsp;podniku - pri určit&yacute;ch činnostiach v&nbsp;podniku sa m&ocirc;žu vyskytn&uacute;ť dilemy, č&iacute; to podnik považuje alebo nepovažuje za etick&eacute;.</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0.86em 0px 1.3em; padding: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #343131; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13px;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0.86em 0px 1.3em; padding: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #343131; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13px;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; zoom: 1;\">Typy etick&yacute;ch k&oacute;dexov:</strong></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0.86em 0px 1.3em; padding: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #343131; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13px;\"><em style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; zoom: 1;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; zoom: 1;\">1.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; A&scaron;piračn&yacute; k&oacute;dex&nbsp;</strong>-</em>&nbsp;je prehľad ide&aacute;lov ku ktor&yacute;m by sa malo smerovať. Každ&yacute; podnik m&aacute; in&eacute; ide&aacute;ly</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0.86em 0px 1.3em; padding: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #343131; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13px;\"><em style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; zoom: 1;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; zoom: 1;\">2.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; V&yacute;chovn&yacute; k&oacute;dex</strong></em>&nbsp;- obsahuje presn&eacute; ustanovenia s&nbsp;konkr&eacute;tnym popisom</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0.86em 0px 1.3em; padding: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #343131; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13px;\"><em style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; zoom: 1;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; zoom: 1;\">3.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Regulačn&yacute; k&oacute;dex</strong></em>&nbsp;- sl&uacute;ži ako z&aacute;klad pre regulovanie sťažnost&iacute;</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0.86em 0px 1.3em; padding: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #343131; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13px;\"><em style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; zoom: 1;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; zoom: 1;\">4.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Odvetvov&eacute; k&oacute;dexy</strong></em>&nbsp;- s&uacute; k&oacute;dexy, ktor&eacute; platia pre určit&eacute; odvetvia. Napr&iacute;klad stavebn&eacute; odvetvia m&ocirc;žu mať in&eacute; etick&eacute; k&oacute;dexy ako potravin&aacute;rske odvetvia &nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0.86em 0px 1.3em; padding: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #343131; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13px;\"><em style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; zoom: 1;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; zoom: 1;\">5.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Profesijne k&oacute;dexy</strong></em>&nbsp;- s&uacute; k&oacute;dexy, ktor&eacute; platia pre určit&uacute; profesiu, napr&iacute;klad je profesijn&yacute; k&oacute;dex &uacute;čtovn&iacute;ka &nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0.86em 0px 1.3em; padding: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #343131; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13px;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0.86em 0px 1.3em; padding: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #343131; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13px;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; zoom: 1;\">D&ocirc;vody pre vytvorenie etick&eacute;ho k&oacute;dexu:</strong></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0.86em 0px 1.3em; padding: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #343131; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13px;\">1.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Chcenie, aby zamestnanci hlboko prem&yacute;&scaron;ľali o&nbsp;cieľoch a&nbsp;hodnot&aacute;ch podniku.</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0.86em 0px 1.3em; padding: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #343131; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13px;\">2.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Etick&yacute; k&oacute;dex, keď je vytvoren&yacute;, m&ocirc;že sl&uacute;žiť na ďal&scaron;iu diskusiu a&nbsp;n&aacute;sledne modifik&aacute;ciu.</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0.86em 0px 1.3em; padding: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #343131; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13px;\">3.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Pomoc pri v&scaron;tepovan&iacute; mor&aacute;lky v&nbsp;pr&iacute;pade prijatia nov&yacute;ch zamestnancov do podniku.</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0.86em 0px 1.3em; padding: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #343131; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13px;\">4.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Pomoc pri odhlalen&iacute; etick&eacute;ho prehre&scaron;ku určit&eacute;ho zamestnanca.</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0.86em 0px 1.3em; padding: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #343131; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13px;\">5.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; D&ocirc;kaz spoločnosti, že firma dodržuje v&scaron;etky etick&eacute; pravidl&aacute; a&nbsp;princ&iacute;py.</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0.86em 0px 1.3em; padding: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #343131; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13px;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0.86em 0px 1.3em; padding: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #343131; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13px;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; zoom: 1;\">Etick&yacute; audit</strong></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0.86em 0px 1.3em; padding: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #343131; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13px;\"><em style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; zoom: 1;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; zoom: 1;\">Etick&yacute; audit</strong></em>&nbsp;poskytuje prehľad o&nbsp;s&uacute;časnej kl&iacute;me podniku.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0.86em 0px 1.3em; padding: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #343131; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13px;\"><em style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; zoom: 1;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; zoom: 1;\">Typy etick&yacute;ch auditov:</strong></em></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0.86em 0px 1.3em; padding: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #343131; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13px;\"><em style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; zoom: 1;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; zoom: 1;\">1.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Audit integrity</strong></em>&nbsp;- umožňuje ohodnotiť 6 etick&yacute;ch n&aacute;vykov v&nbsp;podniku</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0.86em 0px 1.3em; padding: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #343131; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13px;\"><em style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; zoom: 1;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; zoom: 1;\">2.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; R&yacute;chly etick&yacute; test -</strong></em>&nbsp; tento test meria etick&uacute; zhodnosť, mieru podobnosti n&aacute;zorov na mieru etiky v&nbsp;podniku&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0.86em 0px 1.3em; padding: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #343131; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13px;\"><em style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; zoom: 1;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; zoom: 1;\">3.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Odhad mor&aacute;lnych hodn&ocirc;t a&nbsp;zraniteľn&yacute;ch miest -</strong></em>&nbsp;tento etick&yacute; audit sa vyznačuje osobn&yacute;mi pohovormi</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0.86em 0px 1.3em; padding: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #343131; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13px;\">&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0.86em 0px 1.3em; padding: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #343131; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13px;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; zoom: 1;\">Najv&scaron;eobecnej&scaron;ie mor&aacute;lne princ&iacute;py:</strong></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0.86em 0px 1.3em; padding: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #343131; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13px;\"><em style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; zoom: 1;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; zoom: 1;\">1.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Egoizmus</strong></em>&nbsp;- predstavuje typ spr&aacute;vania sa človeka, pri ktorom sa človek riadi podľa svojho konania, podľa svojej mysle. Tento človek nepoč&uacute;va nikoho in&eacute;ho, ide si len za svojim &nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0.86em 0px 1.3em; padding: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #343131; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13px;\"><em style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; zoom: 1;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; zoom: 1;\">2.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Alturizmus</strong></em>&nbsp;- predstavuje typ spr&aacute;vania sa človeka, pri ktorom sa prejavuje u&nbsp;človeku &nbsp;nezi&scaron;tn&aacute; pomoc in&eacute;mu človekovi. Tento človek poč&uacute;va in&eacute;ho človeka a&nbsp;riadi sa t&yacute;mto človekom &nbsp;Tento typ spr&aacute;vania sa je opakom egoizmu</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0.86em 0px 1.3em; padding: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #343131; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13px;\"><em style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; zoom: 1;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; zoom: 1;\">3.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Regulat&iacute;vna funkcia</strong></em>&nbsp;- predstavuje typ spr&aacute;vania sa človeka pri ktorom sa človek usmerňuje v&nbsp;danej soci&aacute;lnej skupine, t.j. prisp&ocirc;sobuje sa k&nbsp;danej skupine ľud&iacute; &nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0.86em 0px 1.3em; padding: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #343131; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13px;\"><em style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; zoom: 1;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; zoom: 1;\">4.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Pozn&aacute;vacia funkcia</strong></em>&nbsp;- ide o&nbsp;n&aacute;jdenie najefekt&iacute;vnej&scaron;ieho etick&eacute;ho konania</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0.86em 0px 1.3em; padding: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #343131; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13px;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0.86em 0px 1.3em; padding: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #343131; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13px;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; zoom: 1;\">Zisk a&nbsp;etika</strong></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0.86em 0px 1.3em; padding: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #343131; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13px;\">Maximaliz&aacute;cia zisku je hlavn&yacute;m mot&iacute;vom fungovania podniku, ale zamestnanci v&nbsp;podniku si musia uvedomiť, že podnikanie nie je len o&nbsp;z&iacute;skavan&iacute; peniazi od z&aacute;kazn&iacute;kov, ide tam aj o&nbsp;in&eacute; veci ako napr&iacute;klad sp&ocirc;sob zaobch&aacute;dzania so z&aacute;kazn&iacute;kmi.&nbsp; &nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0.86em 0px 1.3em; padding: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #343131; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13px;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; zoom: 1;\">Podnikov&aacute; kult&uacute;ra</strong></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0.86em 0px 1.3em; padding: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #343131; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13px;\">Na podnikov&uacute; kult&uacute;ru sa nem&aacute; pozerať ako na bezduch&uacute; organiz&aacute;cia s&nbsp;bezduch&yacute;mi luďmi, ale ako na organizovan&uacute; skupinu ľud&iacute; s&nbsp;určit&yacute;m cieľom.</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0.86em 0px 1.3em; padding: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #343131; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13px;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; zoom: 1;\">Najčastej&scaron;ie poru&scaron;enia etick&yacute;ch noriem:</strong></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0.86em 0px 1.3em; padding: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #343131; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13px;\"><em style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; zoom: 1;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; zoom: 1;\">1.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</strong></em>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<em style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; zoom: 1;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; zoom: 1;\">Klamstvo</strong></em>&nbsp;- podnikateľ by nemal klamať obchodn&yacute;m partnerom, spoločn&iacute;kom ani zamestnancom</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0.86em 0px 1.3em; padding: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #343131; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13px;\"><em style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; zoom: 1;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; zoom: 1;\">2.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Ohov&aacute;ranie</strong></em>&nbsp;- sa t&yacute;ka v&auml;č&scaron;inou konkurencie na z&iacute;skanie v&yacute;hod. M&aacute; veľmi podobn&eacute; znaky s&nbsp;klamstvom</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0.86em 0px 1.3em; padding: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #343131; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13px;\"><em style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; zoom: 1;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; zoom: 1;\">3.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Dobrovoľn&aacute; platobn&aacute; neschopnosť -</strong></em>&nbsp;Podnikateľ si vyber&aacute; spl&aacute;canie z&aacute;v&auml;zkov podľa vlastn&eacute;ho uv&aacute;ženia</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0.86em 0px 1.3em; padding: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #343131; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13px;\"><em style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; zoom: 1;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; zoom: 1;\">4.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Nepriznanie primeranej mzdy zamestnancom -</strong></em>&nbsp;v&nbsp;d&ocirc;sledku vysokej nezamestnanosti a&nbsp;nedostatku pracovn&yacute;ch pr&iacute;ležitosti nie platen&aacute; &uacute;mern&aacute; mzda.</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0.86em 0px 1.3em; padding: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #343131; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13px;\"><em style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; zoom: 1;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; zoom: 1;\">5.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Korupcia</strong></em>&nbsp;- vznik&aacute; pri situaci&aacute;ch, keď o verejn&yacute;ch financi&aacute;ch sa rozhoduje v s&uacute;kromnej osoby alebo os&ocirc;b</p>');
INSERT INTO `referaty` (`referat_id`, `user_id`, `category_id`, `title`, `created_at`, `skola`, `content`) VALUES
(32, 25, 5, 'Propagácia', '2024-01-24 15:39:23', 'VŠ', '<p style=\"margin: 0.86em 0px 1.3em; padding: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #343131; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13px;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; zoom: 1;\">Defin&iacute;cia propag&aacute;cie</strong></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0.86em 0px 1.3em; padding: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #343131; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13px;\"><em style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; zoom: 1;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; zoom: 1;\">Propag&aacute;cia</strong></em>&nbsp;je roz&scaron;irovanie poznatkov o&nbsp;niečo. &nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0.86em 0px 1.3em; padding: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #343131; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13px;\"><em style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; zoom: 1;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; zoom: 1;\">Propag&aacute;cia</strong></em>&nbsp;je sp&ocirc;sob komunik&aacute;cie so z&aacute;kazn&iacute;kmi formou reklamy, let&aacute;kov, brož&uacute;rok, internetu, rozhlasu a&nbsp;telev&iacute;zie.</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0.86em 0px 1.3em; padding: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #343131; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13px;\">Pri propag&aacute;cii d&aacute;vaj&uacute; v&yacute;robcovia inform&aacute;cie z&aacute;kazn&iacute;kom&nbsp; o&nbsp;vlastnostiach, značke, &scaron;t&yacute;le, sp&ocirc;sobe použ&iacute;vania dan&eacute;ho produktu</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0.86em 0px 1.3em; padding: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #343131; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13px;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; zoom: 1;\">Formy propag&aacute;cie:</strong></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0.86em 0px 1.3em; padding: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #343131; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13px;\"><em style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; zoom: 1;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; zoom: 1;\">A)&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Podpora predaja</strong></em>&nbsp;- pri tejto forme propag&aacute;cie v&yacute;robca chce nal&aacute;kať z&aacute;kazn&iacute;ka formou napr&iacute;klad zľavy, rabatu a&nbsp;skonta. Cieľom je, aby z&aacute;kazn&iacute;ka zn&iacute;žen&aacute; cena namotivovala k&uacute;piť produkty.</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0.86em 0px 1.3em; padding: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #343131; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13px;\"><em style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; zoom: 1;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; zoom: 1;\">B)&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Osobn&yacute; predaj</strong></em>&nbsp;- je priamy kontakt medzi z&aacute;kazn&iacute;kom a&nbsp;agentom ( to znamen&aacute; agent v&yacute;robcu sa osobne stretne so z&aacute;kazn&iacute;kom. Agent v&yacute;robcu vnucuje z&aacute;kazn&iacute;ka, aby si k&uacute;pil dan&eacute; produkty a&nbsp;služby.</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0.86em 0px 1.3em; padding: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #343131; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13px;\"><em style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; zoom: 1;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; zoom: 1;\">C)&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Reklama</strong></em>&nbsp;- je forma propag&aacute;cie, kedy z&aacute;kazn&iacute;k porovn&aacute;va viacero konkurentov dan&eacute;ho produktu. Reklama je platen&aacute; a&nbsp;vyskytuje v&nbsp;masovokomunikačn&yacute;ch prostriedkoch.</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0.86em 0px 1.3em; padding: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #343131; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13px;\"><em style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; zoom: 1;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; zoom: 1;\">D)&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Publicita</strong></em>&nbsp;- z&aacute;kladn&yacute;m rozdielom medzi reklamou a&nbsp;publicitou je, že reklama je platen&aacute; a&nbsp;publicita je neplaten&aacute; a&nbsp;vzbudzuje v&auml;č&scaron;iu d&ocirc;veru u&nbsp;z&aacute;kazn&iacute;ka.</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0.86em 0px 1.3em; padding: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #343131; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13px;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; zoom: 1;\">Ciele reklamy sa delia na:</strong></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0.86em 0px 1.3em; padding: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #343131; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13px;\"><em style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; zoom: 1;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; zoom: 1;\">Ekonomick&eacute; ciele</strong></em>&nbsp;- v&yacute;robca sa snaž&iacute; propagovať svoje produkty a&nbsp;služby, t&yacute;m, že chce zv&yacute;&scaron;iť objem predaja a&nbsp;zisk danej firmy, kde produkty a&nbsp;služby dod&aacute;va.</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0.86em 0px 1.3em; padding: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #343131; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13px;\"><em style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; zoom: 1;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; zoom: 1;\">Komunikačn&eacute; ciele</strong></em>&nbsp;- v&yacute;robca sa snaž&iacute; vzbudiť z&aacute;ujem o&nbsp;produkty a&nbsp;služby&nbsp; u&nbsp;z&aacute;kazn&iacute;ka.&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0.86em 0px 1.3em; padding: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #343131; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13px;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; zoom: 1;\">Pravidl&aacute; pri reklame:</strong></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0.86em 0px 1.3em; padding: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #343131; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13px;\"><em style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; zoom: 1;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; zoom: 1;\">1.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Pravdivosť reklamy</strong></em>&nbsp;- inform&aacute;cie o&nbsp;produkte a&nbsp;službe maj&uacute; obsahovať pravdiv&eacute;, skutočn&eacute; inform&aacute;cie</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0.86em 0px 1.3em; padding: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #343131; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13px;\"><em style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; zoom: 1;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; zoom: 1;\">2.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; P&ocirc;sobivosť reklamy</strong></em>&nbsp;- reklama by mala byť v&aacute;biv&aacute; zmyslov&yacute;m org&aacute;nom z&aacute;kazn&iacute;ka, t.j. pr&iacute;jemn&eacute; zvukov&eacute; a&nbsp;vizu&aacute;lne efekty.</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0.86em 0px 1.3em; padding: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #343131; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13px;\"><em style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; zoom: 1;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; zoom: 1;\">3.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Hospod&aacute;rnosť reklamy</strong></em>&nbsp;- na reklamu by nemalo byť vynaložen&yacute;ch pr&iacute;li&scaron; veľa finančn&yacute;ch prostriedkov</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0.86em 0px 1.3em; padding: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #343131; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13px;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; zoom: 1;\">Argumentačn&eacute; polohy reklamy:</strong></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0.86em 0px 1.3em; padding: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #343131; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13px;\"><em style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; zoom: 1;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; zoom: 1;\">A)&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; Hodnotov&aacute; argument&aacute;cia reklamy</strong></em>&nbsp;- komunik&aacute;cia so z&aacute;kazn&iacute;kmi cez hodnoty ak&yacute;mi s&uacute; zdravie, kr&aacute;sa, peniaze</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0.86em 0px 1.3em; padding: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #343131; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13px;\"><em style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; zoom: 1;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; zoom: 1;\">B)&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Emoci&aacute;lna argument&aacute;cia reklamy</strong></em>&nbsp;- komunik&aacute;cia so z&aacute;kazn&iacute;kmi cez em&oacute;cie ak&yacute;mi s&uacute; radosť, sm&uacute;tok, bolesť</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0.86em 0px 1.3em; padding: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #343131; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13px;\"><em style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; zoom: 1;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; zoom: 1;\">C)&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Racion&aacute;lna argument&aacute;cia reklamy</strong></em>&nbsp;- komunik&aacute;cia so z&aacute;kazn&iacute;kmi cez fakty, t.j. z&aacute;kladn&eacute; inform&aacute;cie o&nbsp;produkte a&nbsp;službe ak&yacute;mi s&uacute; cena, kvalita, &scaron;t&yacute;l, značka, sp&ocirc;sob použ&iacute;vania, využitie&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0.86em 0px 1.3em; padding: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #343131; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13px;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; zoom: 1;\">Druhy reklamy podľa zad&aacute;vateľov reklamy:</strong></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0.86em 0px 1.3em; padding: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #343131; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13px;\"><em style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; zoom: 1;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; zoom: 1;\">1.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Individu&aacute;lna reklama</strong></em>&nbsp;- je to reklama 1 pr&aacute;vnickej alebo fyzickej osoby- živnostn&iacute;ka. Napr. reklama na holičsk&uacute; službu</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0.86em 0px 1.3em; padding: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #343131; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13px;\"><em style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; zoom: 1;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; zoom: 1;\">2.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Kolekt&iacute;vna reklama</strong></em>&nbsp;- je to reklama 2 alebo viacer&yacute;ch fyzick&yacute;ch alebo pr&aacute;vnick&yacute;ch os&ocirc;b na určit&yacute; produkt alebo službu.</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0.86em 0px 1.3em; padding: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #343131; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13px;\"><em style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; zoom: 1;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; zoom: 1;\">A)&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Odvetvov&aacute; reklama</strong></em>&nbsp;- je to reklama určit&eacute;ho odvetia, ktor&yacute; pon&uacute;ka rovnak&eacute; alebo podobn&eacute; služby. Napr. odvetvie psychol&oacute;gov si d&aacute; reklamu za du&scaron;evn&eacute; zdravie</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0.86em 0px 1.3em; padding: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #343131; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13px;\"><em style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; zoom: 1;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; zoom: 1;\">B)&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Skupinov&aacute; reklama</strong></em>&nbsp;-&nbsp; je to reklama, pri ktorej vlastne prebieha konkurencia podnikov z&nbsp;rovnak&eacute;ho odvetvia</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0.86em 0px 1.3em; padding: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #343131; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13px;\"><em style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; zoom: 1;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; zoom: 1;\">S&uacute;hrnn&aacute; reklama</strong></em>&nbsp;- naz&yacute;va sa aj odvetvov&aacute; reklama, kde podniky rovnak&eacute;ho alebo podobn&eacute;ho charakteru&nbsp; spolupracuj&uacute; navz&aacute;jom pri propag&aacute;cii rovnak&yacute;ch alebo podobn&yacute;ch produktov a&nbsp;služieb &nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0.86em 0px 1.3em; padding: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #343131; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13px;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; zoom: 1;\">Druhy reklamy podľa subjektu reklamy:</strong></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0.86em 0px 1.3em; padding: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #343131; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13px;\"><em style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; zoom: 1;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; zoom: 1;\">1.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Reklama orientovan&aacute; na 1 subjekt</strong></em>&nbsp;- je to reklama orientovan&aacute; na 1 konkr&eacute;tny podnik napr.&nbsp; na podnik SLOVNAFT, a.s. &nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0.86em 0px 1.3em; padding: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #343131; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13px;\"><em style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; zoom: 1;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; zoom: 1;\">2.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Reklama orientovan&aacute; na viacero podnikateľsk&yacute;ch subjektov</strong></em>&nbsp;- je to reklama orientovan&aacute; na 2 alebo viacer&eacute; podniky.</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0.86em 0px 1.3em; padding: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #343131; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13px;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; zoom: 1;\">Druhy reklamy podľa p&ocirc;sobenia na subjekt reklamy:</strong></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0.86em 0px 1.3em; padding: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #343131; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13px;\"><em style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; zoom: 1;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; zoom: 1;\">A)&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Informat&iacute;vna reklama</strong></em>&nbsp;- je reklama zameran&aacute; na fakty o&nbsp;produkte a službe napr. fakty o&nbsp;kvalite, funkci&aacute;ch, využit&iacute; dan&eacute;ho produktu a&nbsp;služby</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0.86em 0px 1.3em; padding: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #343131; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13px;\"><em style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; zoom: 1;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; zoom: 1;\">B)&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Sugest&iacute;vna reklama</strong></em>&nbsp;- je reklama zameran&aacute; na vyvolanie pocitov, n&aacute;lad u&nbsp;z&aacute;kazn&iacute;ka. Medzi n&aacute;lady u&nbsp;z&aacute;kazn&iacute;ka, ktor&eacute; m&ocirc;že vyvolať patria smiech, plač, &uacute;smev, hnev, zlosť, podr&aacute;ždenie</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0.86em 0px 1.3em; padding: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #343131; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13px;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; zoom: 1;\">Spotrebiteľ</strong></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0.86em 0px 1.3em; padding: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #343131; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13px;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; zoom: 1;\">Spotrebiteľ</strong>&nbsp;je osoba, ktor&aacute; kupuje produkty a&nbsp;služby za určit&uacute; cenu.</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0.86em 0px 1.3em; padding: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #343131; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13px;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; zoom: 1;\">Spotrebiteľov rozdeľujeme na 2 skupiny a&nbsp;to:</strong></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0.86em 0px 1.3em; padding: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #343131; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13px;\"><em style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; zoom: 1;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; zoom: 1;\">Individu&aacute;lny spotrebiteľ</strong></em>&nbsp;- je to fyzick&aacute; osoba, ktor&aacute; kupuje produkty a&nbsp;služby na osobn&uacute; spotrebu. Individu&aacute;lni&nbsp; spotrebitelia s&uacute; dom&aacute;cnosti</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0.86em 0px 1.3em; padding: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #343131; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13px;\"><em style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; zoom: 1;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; zoom: 1;\">Spotrebiteľ ako organiz&aacute;cia</strong></em>&nbsp;- je to fyzick&aacute; alebo pr&aacute;vnicka osoba, ktor&aacute; kupuje produkty a&nbsp;služby na ďal&scaron;&iacute; v&yacute;robn&yacute; proces. T&yacute;mto spotrebiteľom ako organiz&aacute;cia je podnik.</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0.86em 0px 1.3em; padding: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #343131; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13px;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; zoom: 1;\">Faktory, ktor&eacute; ovplyvňuj&uacute; spotrebiteľsk&eacute; spr&aacute;vanie:</strong></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0.86em 0px 1.3em; padding: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #343131; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13px;\"><em style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; zoom: 1;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; zoom: 1;\">A)&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Kult&uacute;rne faktory -</strong></em>&nbsp;predstavuj&uacute; určit&eacute; zvyky a&nbsp;trad&iacute;cie, ktor&eacute; typick&eacute; pre určit&eacute;ho spotrebiteľa napr. zvyky vypl&yacute;vaj&uacute;ce z&nbsp;n&aacute;boženstva</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0.86em 0px 1.3em; padding: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #343131; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13px;\"><em style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; zoom: 1;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; zoom: 1;\">B)&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Osobn&eacute; faktory -</strong></em>&nbsp;predstavuj&uacute; určit&eacute; vlastnosti, charakter spotrebiteľa, ale aj jeho životn&uacute; situ&aacute;ciu. Tam patria faktory osobnosti a&nbsp;pr&iacute;jmu spotrebiteľa</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0.86em 0px 1.3em; padding: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #343131; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13px;\"><em style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; zoom: 1;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; zoom: 1;\">C)&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Psychologick&eacute; faktory -</strong></em>&nbsp;odr&aacute;žaj&uacute; určit&eacute; spr&aacute;vanie spotrebiteľa</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0.86em 0px 1.3em; padding: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #343131; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13px;\"><em style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; zoom: 1;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; zoom: 1;\">D)&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Spoločensk&eacute; faktory -</strong></em>&nbsp;s&uacute; to n&aacute;vyky spotrebiteľa, ktor&eacute; v&scaron;tepuje určit&aacute; skupina obyvateľstva. Napr&iacute;klad n&aacute;vyky, ktor&eacute; v&scaron;tepuj&uacute; rodičia deťom alebo vzdelan&iacute; ľudia deťom.</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0.86em 0px 1.3em; padding: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #343131; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13px;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; zoom: 1;\">Medzi propagačn&eacute; prostriedky patria:</strong></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0.86em 0px 1.3em; padding: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #343131; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13px;\"><em style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; zoom: 1;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; zoom: 1;\">A)&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; Plag&aacute;t</strong></em>&nbsp;- &uacute;lohou plag&aacute;tu je obozn&aacute;miť v&nbsp;kr&aacute;tkom čase z&aacute;kazn&iacute;ka o&nbsp;dan&yacute;ch produktoch a&nbsp;služb&aacute;ch &nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0.86em 0px 1.3em; padding: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #343131; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13px;\"><em style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; zoom: 1;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; zoom: 1;\">B)&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Katal&oacute;g</strong></em>&nbsp;- je abecedn&yacute; zoznam produktov a&nbsp;služieb, ktor&eacute; podnik pon&uacute;ka</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0.86em 0px 1.3em; padding: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #343131; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13px;\"><em style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; zoom: 1;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; zoom: 1;\">C)&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Prospekt</strong></em>&nbsp;- informuje z&aacute;kazn&iacute;ka o&nbsp;vlastnostiach produktu</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0.86em 0px 1.3em; padding: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #343131; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13px;\"><em style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; zoom: 1;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; zoom: 1;\">D)&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Skladačka</strong></em>&nbsp;- je to vlastne prospekt, ale je prospekt, ktor&yacute; je usporiadan&yacute; do geometrick&yacute;ch tvarov</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0.86em 0px 1.3em; padding: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #343131; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13px;\"><em style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; zoom: 1;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; zoom: 1;\">E)&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Let&aacute;k</strong></em>&nbsp;- informuje z&aacute;kazn&iacute;ka o&nbsp;zaveden&iacute; produktu a&nbsp;služby do prev&aacute;dzky</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0.86em 0px 1.3em; padding: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #343131; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13px;\"><em style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; zoom: 1;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; zoom: 1;\">F)&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Transparenty</strong></em>&nbsp;- s&uacute; spoločn&iacute;kom potenci&aacute;lnych z&aacute;kazn&iacute;kov pri cestovan&iacute;.&nbsp;&nbsp;</p>');
INSERT INTO `referaty` (`referat_id`, `user_id`, `category_id`, `title`, `created_at`, `skola`, `content`) VALUES
(33, 25, 5, 'Trh', '2024-01-24 15:39:46', 'VŠ', '<p style=\"margin: 0.86em 0px 1.3em; padding: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #343131; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13px;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; zoom: 1;\">Trh</strong>&nbsp;je miesto, kde sa stret&aacute;vaj&uacute; kupuj&uacute;ci a&nbsp;pred&aacute;vaj&uacute;ci za &uacute;čelom v&yacute;meny produktov a&nbsp;služieb a&nbsp;za &uacute;čelom dohodnutia sa na cene produktov a&nbsp;služieb.</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0.86em 0px 1.3em; padding: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #343131; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13px;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; zoom: 1;\">A)&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Podľa počtu pred&aacute;van&yacute;ch produktov a&nbsp;služieb sa trh del&iacute; na:</strong></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0.86em 0px 1.3em; padding: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #343131; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13px;\"><em style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; zoom: 1;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; zoom: 1;\">1.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Čiastkov&yacute; trh</strong></em>&nbsp;- je to trh, ktor&yacute; sa vyznačuje jedn&yacute;m &scaron;pecifick&yacute;m produktom a&nbsp;službou.</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0.86em 0px 1.3em; padding: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #343131; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13px;\"><em style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; zoom: 1;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; zoom: 1;\">2.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Agreg&aacute;tny trh</strong></em>&nbsp;- je to trh v&scaron;etk&yacute;ch tovarov a&nbsp;služieb.</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0.86em 0px 1.3em; padding: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #343131; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13px;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; zoom: 1;\">B)&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Podľa predmetu k&uacute;py a&nbsp;predaja sa del&iacute; na:</strong></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0.86em 0px 1.3em; padding: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #343131; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13px;\"><em style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; zoom: 1;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; zoom: 1;\">1.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Trh tovarov a&nbsp;služieb</strong></em>&nbsp;- určen&yacute;ch na osobn&uacute; spotrebu</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0.86em 0px 1.3em; padding: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #343131; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13px;\"><em style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; zoom: 1;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; zoom: 1;\">2.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Trh v&yacute;robn&yacute;ch faktorov</strong></em>&nbsp;- je to trh pr&aacute;ce, p&ocirc;dy a&nbsp;kapit&aacute;lu</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0.86em 0px 1.3em; padding: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #343131; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13px;\"><em style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; zoom: 1;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; zoom: 1;\">3.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Finančn&yacute; trh</strong></em>&nbsp;- tam patr&iacute; kapit&aacute;lov&yacute;, poistn&yacute;, dev&iacute;zov&yacute; trh, trh drah&yacute;ch kovov</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0.86em 0px 1.3em; padding: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #343131; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13px;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; zoom: 1;\">C)&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Z&nbsp;&uacute;zemn&eacute;ho hľadiska sa trh del&iacute; na:</strong></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0.86em 0px 1.3em; padding: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #343131; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13px;\"><em style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; zoom: 1;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; zoom: 1;\">1.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Miestny trh</strong></em>&nbsp;&ndash; Miestny trh sa naz&yacute;va aj region&aacute;lny trh.</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0.86em 0px 1.3em; padding: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #343131; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13px;\"><em style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; zoom: 1;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; zoom: 1;\">2.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; N&aacute;rodn&yacute; trh</strong></em>&nbsp;- N&aacute;rodn&yacute; trh vznikol zoskupen&iacute;m miestnych ( region&aacute;lnych) trhov &nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0.86em 0px 1.3em; padding: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #343131; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13px;\"><em style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; zoom: 1;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; zoom: 1;\">3.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Medzin&aacute;rodn&yacute; &nbsp;trh</strong></em>&nbsp;-&nbsp; Medzin&aacute;rodn&yacute; trh vznikol zoskupen&iacute;m n&aacute;rodn&yacute;ch trhov&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0.86em 0px 1.3em; padding: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #343131; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13px;\"><em style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; zoom: 1;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; zoom: 1;\">4.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Svetov&yacute; trh</strong></em>&nbsp;- je to s&uacute;bor v&scaron;etk&yacute;ch trhov na svete</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0.86em 0px 1.3em; padding: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #343131; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13px;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; zoom: 1;\">Charakteristika dopytu a&nbsp;ponuky</strong></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0.86em 0px 1.3em; padding: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #343131; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13px;\"><em style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; zoom: 1;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; zoom: 1;\">Dopyt</strong></em>&nbsp;je množstvo tovarov a&nbsp;služieb, ktor&eacute; s&uacute; ochotn&iacute; kupuj&uacute;ci &nbsp;k&uacute;piť za určit&uacute; cenu. &nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0.86em 0px 1.3em; padding: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #343131; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13px;\"><em style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; zoom: 1;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; zoom: 1;\">Ponuka</strong></em>&nbsp;je množstvo tovarov a&nbsp;služieb, ktor&eacute; s&uacute; ochotn&iacute; pred&aacute;vaj&uacute;ci predať za určit&uacute; cenu.</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0.86em 0px 1.3em; padding: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #343131; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13px;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; zoom: 1;\">Trhov&eacute; subjekty</strong></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0.86em 0px 1.3em; padding: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #343131; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13px;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; zoom: 1;\">Medzi trhov&eacute; subjekty patria dom&aacute;cnosti, podniky a&nbsp;&scaron;t&aacute;t.</strong></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0.86em 0px 1.3em; padding: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #343131; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13px;\"><em style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; zoom: 1;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; zoom: 1;\">A)&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Dom&aacute;cnosti</strong></em>&nbsp;- kupuj&uacute; statky a&nbsp;služby a&nbsp;pred&aacute;vaj&uacute; v&yacute;robn&eacute; faktory ( pr&aacute;ca, p&ocirc;da, kapit&aacute;l).</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0.86em 0px 1.3em; padding: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #343131; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13px;\"><em style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; zoom: 1;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; zoom: 1;\">B)&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Podniky</strong></em>&nbsp;- kupuj&uacute; v&yacute;robn&eacute; faktory ( pr&aacute;ca, p&ocirc;da, kapit&aacute;l) a&nbsp;pred&aacute;vaj&uacute; statky a&nbsp;služby.</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0.86em 0px 1.3em; padding: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #343131; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13px;\"><em style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; zoom: 1;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; zoom: 1;\">C)&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &Scaron;t&aacute;t</strong></em>&nbsp;- je zvl&aacute;&scaron;tnym subjektom na trhu. Na trhu vystupuje ako pred&aacute;vaj&uacute;ci ( predaj &scaron;t&aacute;tnych oblig&aacute;cii), ale aj ako kupuj&uacute;ci (vl&aacute;dne v&yacute;davky)</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0.86em 0px 1.3em; padding: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #343131; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13px;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; zoom: 1;\">Veličiny trhu</strong></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0.86em 0px 1.3em; padding: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #343131; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13px;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; zoom: 1;\">Medzi veličiny trhu patria trhov&yacute; potenci&aacute;l, trhov&aacute; kapacita, stupeň nas&yacute;tenia trhu, trhov&yacute; podiel, relat&iacute;vny trhov&yacute; podiel:</strong></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0.86em 0px 1.3em; padding: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #343131; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13px;\"><em style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; zoom: 1;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; zoom: 1;\">A)&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Trhov&yacute; potenci&aacute;l</strong></em>&nbsp;- predstavuje najvy&scaron;&scaron;&iacute; možn&yacute; dopyt, ktor&yacute; sa m&ocirc;že vyprodukovať za určit&eacute; obdobie.</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0.86em 0px 1.3em; padding: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #343131; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13px;\"><em style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; zoom: 1;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; zoom: 1;\">B)&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Trhov&aacute; kapacita</strong></em>&nbsp;- predstavuje celkov&yacute; odbyt pred&aacute;vaj&uacute;cich.</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0.86em 0px 1.3em; padding: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #343131; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13px;\"><em style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; zoom: 1;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; zoom: 1;\">C)&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Stupeň nas&yacute;tenia trhu</strong></em>&nbsp;- predstavuje pomer medzi trhovou kapacitou a&nbsp;trhov&yacute;m potenci&aacute;lom.</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0.86em 0px 1.3em; padding: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #343131; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13px;\"><em style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; zoom: 1;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; zoom: 1;\">D)&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Trhov&yacute; podiel</strong></em>&nbsp;- vyjadruje ak&eacute; siln&eacute; je postavenie v&yacute;robku v&nbsp;porovnan&iacute; s&nbsp;konkurenčn&yacute;mi v&yacute;robkami.</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0.86em 0px 1.3em; padding: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #343131; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13px;\"><em style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; zoom: 1;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; zoom: 1;\">E)&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; Relat&iacute;vny trhov&yacute; podiel</strong></em>&nbsp;- vyjadruje pomer medzi trhov&yacute;m podielom k&nbsp;podielu najv&auml;č&scaron;ieho konkurenta.</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0.86em 0px 1.3em; padding: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #343131; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13px;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; zoom: 1;\">Konkurencia</strong>&nbsp;- predstavuj&uacute; podniky, ktor&eacute; poskytuj&uacute; produkty a&nbsp;služby rovnak&eacute;ho alebo podobn&eacute;ho charakteru.</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0.86em 0px 1.3em; padding: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #343131; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13px;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; zoom: 1;\">Medzi 4 &uacute;rovne konkurencie patria konkurencia značiek, konkurencia odvetvia, konkurencia formy a&nbsp;konkurencia rodu.</strong></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0.86em 0px 1.3em; padding: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #343131; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13px;\"><em style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; zoom: 1;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; zoom: 1;\">A)&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Konkurencia značiek</strong></em>&nbsp;- podnik považuje za konkurentov tie podniky, ktor&eacute; pon&uacute;kaj&uacute; rovnak&eacute; alebo podobn&eacute; v&yacute;robky a&nbsp;statky rovnak&eacute;mu z&aacute;kazn&iacute;kovi za rovnak&uacute; cenu</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0.86em 0px 1.3em; padding: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #343131; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13px;\"><em style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; zoom: 1;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; zoom: 1;\">B)&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Konkurencia odvetia</strong></em>&nbsp;- podnik považuje za konkurentov v&yacute;robcov&nbsp; tej istej rady, t.j. v&yacute;robcov, ktor&yacute; pon&uacute;kaj&uacute; rovnak&eacute; statky</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0.86em 0px 1.3em; padding: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #343131; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13px;\"><em style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; zoom: 1;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; zoom: 1;\">C)&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Konkurencia formy</strong></em>&nbsp;- podnik považuje za konkurentov v&yacute;robcov, ktor&iacute; pon&uacute;kaj&uacute; rovnak&eacute; služby.</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0.86em 0px 1.3em; padding: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #343131; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13px;\"><em style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; zoom: 1;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; zoom: 1;\">D)&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Konkurencia rodu</strong></em>&nbsp;-&nbsp; podnik, ktor&yacute; bojuje o&nbsp;každ&eacute;ho z&aacute;kazn&iacute;ka a&nbsp;za jeho peniaze</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0.86em 0px 1.3em; padding: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #343131; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13px;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; zoom: 1;\">Konkurencia z&nbsp;hľadiska subjektami sa del&iacute; na:</strong></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0.86em 0px 1.3em; padding: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #343131; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13px;\"><em style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; zoom: 1;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; zoom: 1;\">A)&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Konkurenciu na strane dopytu (konkurencia dopytov&aacute;)</strong></em>&nbsp;- predstavuje konkurenciu medzi spotrebiteľmi.</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0.86em 0px 1.3em; padding: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #343131; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13px;\"><em style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; zoom: 1;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; zoom: 1;\">B)&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;Konkurencia na strane ponuky (konkurencia ponukov&aacute;)</strong></em>&nbsp;- predstavuje konkurenciu medzi pred&aacute;vaj&uacute;cimi.</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0.86em 0px 1.3em; padding: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #343131; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13px;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; zoom: 1;\">Konkurencia podľa formy predaja sa del&iacute; na:</strong></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0.86em 0px 1.3em; padding: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #343131; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13px;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; zoom: 1;\">Cenov&aacute; konkurencia</strong>&nbsp;- v&yacute;robca s&uacute;per&iacute; t&yacute;m sp&ocirc;sobom, že&nbsp; &nbsp;sa vzd&aacute; časti zisku, t&yacute;m, že zn&iacute;ži ceny svojich pon&uacute;kan&yacute;ch v&yacute;robkov a&nbsp;služieb.</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0.86em 0px 1.3em; padding: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #343131; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13px;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; zoom: 1;\">Necenov&aacute; konkurencia</strong>&nbsp;- v&yacute;robca s&uacute;per&iacute; t&yacute;m sp&ocirc;sobom, že zv&yacute;&scaron;i kvalitu a&nbsp;technick&eacute; parametre&nbsp; svojich pon&uacute;kan&yacute;ch v&yacute;robkov a&nbsp;služieb.</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0.86em 0px 1.3em; padding: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #343131; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13px;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; zoom: 1;\">Konkurencia podľa trhov&yacute;ch subjektov na:</strong></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0.86em 0px 1.3em; padding: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #343131; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13px;\"><em style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; zoom: 1;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; zoom: 1;\">1.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Dokonal&uacute; konkurenciu</strong></em>&nbsp;- t&aacute;to konkurencia v&scaron;ak v&nbsp;re&aacute;lnej praxi neexistuje. V&yacute;robcovia pri tejto konkurencii dod&aacute;vaj&uacute; nič&iacute;m nel&iacute;&scaron;iace produkty a&nbsp;službu. Jedinou met&oacute;dou pri konkurenčnom boji je znižovanie v&yacute;robn&yacute;ch n&aacute;kladov.</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0.86em 0px 1.3em; padding: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #343131; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13px;\"><em style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; zoom: 1;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; zoom: 1;\">2.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Nedokonal&uacute; konkurenciu</strong></em>&nbsp;- je opakom dokonalej konkurencie. Podstatn&yacute; rozdiel je v&nbsp;tom, že jednotliv&yacute; v&yacute;robca m&ocirc;že ovplyvniť cenu na trhu.</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0.86em 0px 1.3em; padding: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #343131; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13px;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; zoom: 1;\">Nedokonal&aacute; konkurencia sa del&iacute; na:</strong></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0.86em 0px 1.3em; padding: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #343131; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13px;\"><em style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; zoom: 1;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; zoom: 1;\">A)&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Monopol</strong></em>&nbsp;- na trhu existuje jedin&yacute; v&yacute;robca určit&eacute;ho druhu v&yacute;robku a&nbsp;služby</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0.86em 0px 1.3em; padding: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #343131; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13px;\"><em style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; zoom: 1;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; zoom: 1;\">B)&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;Oligopol</strong></em>&nbsp;-&nbsp;&nbsp; na trhu existuj&uacute; niekoľk&iacute; v&yacute;robcovia na trhu určit&eacute;ho druhu v&yacute;robku a&nbsp;služby, ktor&yacute; svojou činnosťou nedovolia vst&uacute;piť na trh ďal&scaron;&iacute;m v&yacute;robcom&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0.86em 0px 1.3em; padding: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #343131; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13px;\"><em style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; zoom: 1;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; zoom: 1;\">C)&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Monopolistick&uacute; konkurenciu</strong></em>&nbsp;- na trhu je veľa v&yacute;robcov. Ten ist&yacute; tovar od r&ocirc;znych v&yacute;robcov&nbsp; sa odli&scaron;uje obalom, farbou a&nbsp;dizajnom&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0.86em 0px 1.3em; padding: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #343131; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13px;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; zoom: 1;\">Benchmarking</strong></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0.86em 0px 1.3em; padding: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #343131; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13px;\"><em style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; zoom: 1;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; zoom: 1;\">Benchmarking</strong></em>&nbsp;je porovnanie tovarov, služieb, podnikateľskej aktivity prostredn&iacute;ctvom parametrov v&nbsp;porovnan&iacute; s&nbsp;in&yacute;mi konkurenčn&yacute;mi podnikmi.</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0.86em 0px 1.3em; padding: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #343131; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13px;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; zoom: 1;\">Marketingov&yacute; v&yacute;skum sa del&iacute; na 2 druhy, a&nbsp;to:</strong></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0.86em 0px 1.3em; padding: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #343131; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13px;\"><em style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; zoom: 1;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; zoom: 1;\">A)&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; V&yacute;skum ekoskopick&yacute;</strong></em>&nbsp;- v&yacute;skum ekoskopick&yacute; sa zaober&aacute; presne merateľn&yacute;mi veličinami napr. cena, obrat, predaj, počet kupuj&uacute;cich.&nbsp; &nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0.86em 0px 1.3em; padding: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #343131; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13px;\"><em style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; zoom: 1;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; zoom: 1;\">B)&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; V&yacute;skum demoskopick&yacute;</strong></em>&nbsp;- v&yacute;skum deskopick&aacute; sa zaober&aacute; nemerateľn&yacute;mi veličinami napr. spr&aacute;van&iacute;m sa spotrebiteľov na trhu, ich jednan&iacute;m a&nbsp;reakciami.&nbsp;&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0.86em 0px 1.3em; padding: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #343131; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13px;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; zoom: 1;\">Postup pri v&yacute;skume trhu:</strong></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0.86em 0px 1.3em; padding: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #343131; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13px;\"><em style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; zoom: 1;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; zoom: 1;\">1.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Cieľ v&yacute;skumu</strong></em>&nbsp;- v&nbsp;tejto f&aacute;ze sa definuje v&yacute;skumn&yacute; probl&eacute;m.</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0.86em 0px 1.3em; padding: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #343131; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13px;\"><em style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; zoom: 1;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; zoom: 1;\">2.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Zdroje &uacute;dajov</strong></em>&nbsp;- v&nbsp;tejto f&aacute;ze sa definuj&uacute; z&aacute;kladn&eacute; požiadavky na potrebn&eacute; inform&aacute;cie., d&aacute;ta a&nbsp;ich zdroje. Zdroje m&ocirc;žu byť intern&eacute;, extern&eacute;, sekund&aacute;rne a&nbsp;prim&aacute;rne.</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0.86em 0px 1.3em; padding: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #343131; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13px;\"><em style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; zoom: 1;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; zoom: 1;\">3.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Met&oacute;da v&yacute;skumu</strong></em>&nbsp;- určuje ak&yacute;m sp&ocirc;sobom sa vykon&aacute;va dan&yacute; v&yacute;skum.</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0.86em 0px 1.3em; padding: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #343131; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13px;\"><em style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; zoom: 1;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; zoom: 1;\">4.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Pr&iacute;prava v&yacute;skumn&eacute;ho projektu</strong></em>&nbsp;- v&nbsp;tejto f&aacute;ze sa pripravuje v&yacute;skumn&yacute; projekt organizačne</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0.86em 0px 1.3em; padding: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #343131; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13px;\"><em style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; zoom: 1;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; zoom: 1;\">5.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Určenie veľkosti vzorky</strong></em>&nbsp;- V&yacute;ber m&ocirc;že byť n&aacute;hodn&yacute; alebo cielen&yacute;</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0.86em 0px 1.3em; padding: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #343131; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13px;\"><em style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; zoom: 1;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; zoom: 1;\">6.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Zber d&aacute;t</strong></em>&nbsp;- pri zbere d&aacute;t je potrebn&aacute; pripravenosť zamestnancov, aby nedo&scaron;lo k&nbsp;chybe</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0.86em 0px 1.3em; padding: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #343131; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13px;\"><em style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; zoom: 1;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; zoom: 1;\">7.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Anal&yacute;za a&nbsp;spracovanie d&aacute;t</strong></em>&nbsp;- t&uacute;to f&aacute;zu vykon&aacute;vaj&uacute; &scaron;peci&aacute;lne vy&scaron;kolen&iacute; pracovn&iacute;ci</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0.86em 0px 1.3em; padding: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #343131; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13px;\"><em style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; zoom: 1;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; zoom: 1;\">8.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Implement&aacute;cia v&yacute;sledkov v&yacute;skumu, odporučenia</strong></em>&nbsp;- v&nbsp;tejto f&aacute;ze sa vypracov&aacute;va &scaron;peci&aacute;lna v&yacute;skumn&aacute; spr&aacute;va</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0.86em 0px 1.3em; padding: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #343131; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13px;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; zoom: 1;\">Zdroje &uacute;dajov sa delia na prim&aacute;rne, sekund&aacute;rne, intern&eacute; extern&eacute;...</strong></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0.86em 0px 1.3em; padding: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #343131; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13px;\"><em style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; zoom: 1;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; zoom: 1;\">A)&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; Prim&aacute;rne zdroje &uacute;dajov -</strong></em>&nbsp;s&uacute; zbieran&eacute; v&nbsp;s&uacute;vislosti s&nbsp;konkr&eacute;tnym probl&eacute;mom.</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0.86em 0px 1.3em; padding: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #343131; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13px;\"><em style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; zoom: 1;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; zoom: 1;\">B)&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Sekund&aacute;rne zdroje &uacute;dajov</strong></em>&nbsp;- s&uacute; zdroje &uacute;dajov, ktor&eacute; nes&uacute;visia s&nbsp;konkr&eacute;tnym probl&eacute;mom.</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0.86em 0px 1.3em; padding: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #343131; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13px;\"><em style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; zoom: 1;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; zoom: 1;\">C)&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Vn&uacute;torn&eacute; (intern&eacute;) zdroje &uacute;dajov -</strong></em>&nbsp;Tieto inform&aacute;cie s&uacute; s&nbsp;podnikom &uacute;zko spojen&eacute;</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0.86em 0px 1.3em; padding: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #343131; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13px;\"><em style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; zoom: 1;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; zoom: 1;\">D)&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; Vonkaj&scaron;ie (extern&eacute;) zdroje &uacute;dajov</strong></em>&nbsp;- v&nbsp;na&scaron;ich podmienkach je to v&nbsp;podstate zabezpečovan&eacute; z&aacute;konom o&nbsp;&scaron;tatistike.</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0.86em 0px 1.3em; padding: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #343131; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13px;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; zoom: 1;\">Met&oacute;dy v&yacute;skumu trhu</strong></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0.86em 0px 1.3em; padding: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #343131; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13px;\">Medzi met&oacute;dy v&yacute;skumu trhu patria prim&aacute;rne a&nbsp;sekund&aacute;rne met&oacute;dy v&yacute;skumu trhu</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0.86em 0px 1.3em; padding: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #343131; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13px;\"><em style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; zoom: 1;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; zoom: 1;\">1.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Sekund&aacute;rny v&yacute;skum</strong></em>&nbsp;- je v&yacute;skum zabezpečovan&yacute; zo stola</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0.86em 0px 1.3em; padding: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #343131; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13px;\"><em style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; zoom: 1;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; zoom: 1;\">2.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Prim&aacute;rny v&yacute;skum</strong></em>&nbsp;- je v&yacute;skum zabezpečovan&yacute; z&nbsp;ter&eacute;nu</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0.86em 0px 1.3em; padding: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #343131; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13px;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; zoom: 1;\">Medzi ďal&scaron;ie met&oacute;dy v&yacute;skumu trhu patria:</strong></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0.86em 0px 1.3em; padding: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #343131; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13px;\"><em style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; zoom: 1;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; zoom: 1;\">1.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Pozorovanie</strong></em>&nbsp;- je cieľavedom&eacute; a&nbsp;pl&aacute;novit&eacute; zhromažďovanie &uacute;dajov</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0.86em 0px 1.3em; padding: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #343131; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13px;\"><em style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; zoom: 1;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; zoom: 1;\">2.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Osobn&eacute; dopytovanie (interview)</strong></em>&nbsp;- je najpouž&iacute;vanej&scaron;ia met&oacute;da v&yacute;skumu trhu prostredn&iacute;ctvom dopytovania. Toto interview m&ocirc;že byť vopred pripraven&eacute; alebo veden&eacute; voľn&yacute;m rozhovorom.</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0.86em 0px 1.3em; padding: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #343131; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13px;\"><em style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; zoom: 1;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; zoom: 1;\">3.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; P&iacute;somn&eacute; dopytovanie</strong></em>&nbsp;- komunik&aacute;cia prebieha prostredn&iacute;ctvom dotazn&iacute;ka, nie je potrebn&aacute; pr&iacute;tomnosť &uacute;častn&iacute;kov rozhovoru.</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0.86em 0px 1.3em; padding: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #343131; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13px;\"><em style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; zoom: 1;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; zoom: 1;\">4.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Experiment</strong></em>&nbsp;- sk&uacute;maj&uacute; sa veci, javy alebo určit&eacute; situ&aacute;cie za vopred stanoven&yacute;ch podmienok</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0.86em 0px 1.3em; padding: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #343131; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13px;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; zoom: 1;\">Experiment m&ocirc;že byť:</strong></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0.86em 0px 1.3em; padding: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #343131; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13px;\"><em style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; zoom: 1;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; zoom: 1;\">A)&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; Laborat&oacute;rny</strong></em>&nbsp;- s&uacute; vykon&aacute;van&eacute; v&nbsp;laborat&oacute;rnych podmienkach, kde s&uacute; v&scaron;etky veci izolovan&eacute; okrem hlavn&eacute;ho&nbsp; predmetu experimentu</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0.86em 0px 1.3em; padding: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #343131; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13px;\"><em style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; zoom: 1;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; zoom: 1;\">B)&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Ter&eacute;nny</strong></em>&nbsp;- vykon&aacute;va sa v&nbsp;prirodzen&yacute;ch podmienkach trhu</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0.86em 0px 1.3em; padding: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #343131; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13px;\"><em style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; zoom: 1;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; zoom: 1;\">5.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Panel</strong></em>&nbsp;- je st&aacute;ly reprezentat&iacute;vny okruh respodentov, ktor&iacute; odpovedaj&uacute; v&nbsp;pravideln&yacute;ch intervaloch na rovnak&eacute; ot&aacute;zky.</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0.86em 0px 1.3em; padding: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #343131; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13px;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; zoom: 1;\">Z&aacute;kazn&iacute;ci</strong></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0.86em 0px 1.3em; padding: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #343131; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13px;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; zoom: 1;\">Trhy z&aacute;kazn&iacute;kov sa delia na nasleduj&uacute;ce trhy:</strong></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0.86em 0px 1.3em; padding: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #343131; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13px;\"><em style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; zoom: 1;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; zoom: 1;\">A)&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; Trhy spotrebiteľov</strong></em>&nbsp;- s&uacute; to dom&aacute;cnosti, ktor&eacute; kupuj&uacute; statky a&nbsp;služby pre svoju vlastn&uacute; osobn&uacute; spotrebu.</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0.86em 0px 1.3em; padding: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #343131; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13px;\"><em style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; zoom: 1;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; zoom: 1;\">B)&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Trhy v&yacute;robnej sf&eacute;ry</strong></em>&nbsp;- s&uacute; to podniky, ktor&eacute; kupuj&uacute; statky a&nbsp;služby pre svoj vlastn&yacute; v&yacute;robn&yacute; proces.</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0.86em 0px 1.3em; padding: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #343131; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13px;\"><em style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; zoom: 1;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; zoom: 1;\">C)&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Trhy spostredkovateľov</strong></em>&nbsp;- s&uacute; to trhov&eacute; subjekty, ktor&eacute; kupuj&uacute; statky a&nbsp;služby za &uacute;čelom ich op&auml;tovn&eacute;ho predaja za &uacute;čelom zisku.</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0.86em 0px 1.3em; padding: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #343131; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13px;\"><em style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; zoom: 1;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; zoom: 1;\">D)&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; Medzin&aacute;rodn&eacute; trhy</strong></em>&nbsp;- medzi medzin&aacute;rodn&eacute; trhy patria spotrebitelia, v&yacute;robcovia, sprostredkovatelia a&nbsp;vl&aacute;dy</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0.86em 0px 1.3em; padding: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #343131; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13px;\"><em style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; zoom: 1;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; zoom: 1;\">E)&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Vl&aacute;dne trhy</strong></em>&nbsp;- vl&aacute;dne in&scaron;tit&uacute;cie a&nbsp;org&aacute;ny, ktor&eacute; nakupuj&uacute; statky a&nbsp;služby za &uacute;čelom verejn&yacute;ch služieb.</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0.86em 0px 1.3em; padding: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #343131; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13px;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; zoom: 1;\">Z&aacute;kazn&iacute;ci sa ďalej delia na vn&uacute;torn&yacute;ch a&nbsp;vonkaj&scaron;&iacute;ch z&aacute;kazn&iacute;kov...</strong></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0.86em 0px 1.3em; padding: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #343131; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13px;\"><em style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; zoom: 1;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; zoom: 1;\">A)&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; Vn&uacute;torn&iacute; z&aacute;kazn&iacute;ci</strong></em>&nbsp;- zamestnanci, ktor&iacute; napĺňaj&uacute; predstavy podniku &nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0.86em 0px 1.3em; padding: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #343131; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13px;\"><em style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; zoom: 1;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; zoom: 1;\">B)&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Vonkaj&scaron;&iacute; z&aacute;kazn&iacute;ci</strong></em>&nbsp;- tam patria samotn&iacute; z&aacute;kazn&iacute;ci a&nbsp;objedn&aacute;vatelia služieb</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0.86em 0px 1.3em; padding: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #343131; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13px;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; zoom: 1;\">Segment&aacute;cia trhu sa del&iacute; na:</strong></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0.86em 0px 1.3em; padding: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #343131; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13px;\"><em style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; zoom: 1;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; zoom: 1;\">A)&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; Geografick&uacute; segment&aacute;ciu trhu</strong></em>&nbsp;- je to členenie trhu na r&ocirc;zne geografick&eacute; regi&oacute;ny napr. na &scaron;t&aacute;ty, regi&oacute;ny, mest&aacute; a&nbsp;dediny</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0.86em 0px 1.3em; padding: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #343131; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13px;\"><em style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; zoom: 1;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; zoom: 1;\">B)&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Demografick&uacute; segment&aacute;ciu trhu</strong></em>&nbsp;- je to rozdelenie trhu na skupiny z&aacute;kazn&iacute;kov podľa veku, pohlavia, povolania, vzdelania</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0.86em 0px 1.3em; padding: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #343131; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13px;\"><em style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; zoom: 1;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; zoom: 1;\">C)&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Psychografick&uacute; segment&aacute;ciu trhu</strong></em>&nbsp;- je to rozdelenie trhu podľa soci&aacute;lnych vrstiev, životn&eacute;ho &scaron;t&yacute;lu a&nbsp;osobnosti</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0.86em 0px 1.3em; padding: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #343131; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13px;\"><em style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; zoom: 1;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; zoom: 1;\">D)&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Psychologick&uacute; segment&aacute;ciu trhu</strong></em>&nbsp;- je to rozdeleniu trhu podľa znalosti o&nbsp;v&yacute;robku, postoja k&nbsp;v&yacute;robku, ich použitia alebo reakcie na v&yacute;robok</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0.86em 0px 1.3em; padding: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #343131; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13px;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; zoom: 1;\">Pojmy pri psychologickej segment&aacute;cii</strong></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0.86em 0px 1.3em; padding: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #343131; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13px;\"><em style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; zoom: 1;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; zoom: 1;\">A)&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; Pr&iacute;ležitosti</strong></em>&nbsp;- z&aacute;kazn&iacute;kov treba rozli&scaron;ovať podľa toho pri ak&yacute;ch pr&iacute;ležitostiach vznikaj&uacute; ich priania a&nbsp;potreby.</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0.86em 0px 1.3em; padding: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #343131; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13px;\"><em style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; zoom: 1;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; zoom: 1;\">B)&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &Uacute;žitky</strong></em>&nbsp;&ndash; tam patria zdravotn&eacute; &uacute;žitky, kozmetick&eacute; &uacute;žitky, pr&iacute;jemn&aacute; chuť</p>');
INSERT INTO `referaty` (`referat_id`, `user_id`, `category_id`, `title`, `created_at`, `skola`, `content`) VALUES
(34, 25, 5, 'Cena', '2024-01-24 15:40:06', 'VŠ', '<p style=\"margin: 0.86em 0px 1.3em; padding: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #343131; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13px;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; zoom: 1;\">Cena</strong>&nbsp;je peňažn&eacute; vyjadrenie hodnoty produktov a&nbsp;služieb, vyjadren&aacute; v&nbsp;peniazoch danej meny a&nbsp;určen&aacute; v&yacute;robcom ku konečn&eacute;mu spotrebiteľovi.</p>\r\n<h2 style=\"margin: 1.3em 0px 0px; padding: 0px; zoom: 1; font-weight: normal; line-height: 1.3em; font-size: 2em; color: #343131; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; zoom: 1;\">1.&nbsp; &nbsp;Intern&eacute; faktory stanovenia cien</strong></h2>\r\n<h4 style=\"margin: 1.3em 0px 0px; padding: 0px; zoom: 1; font-weight: normal; line-height: 1.3em; font-size: 1.5em; color: #343131; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; zoom: 1;\">A)&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Ciele marketingu &nbsp;&nbsp;</strong></h4>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0.86em 0px 1.3em; padding: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #343131; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13px;\"><em style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; zoom: 1;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; zoom: 1;\">1.&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;Prežitie</strong></em>&nbsp;- tento cieľ sa uplatňuje, keď podnik m&aacute; ťažkosti. V&nbsp;tomto pr&iacute;pade mu nejde o&nbsp;nič in&eacute; iba o&nbsp;to, aby nezanikol</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0.86em 0px 1.3em; padding: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #343131; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13px;\"><em style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; zoom: 1;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; zoom: 1;\">2.&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;Maximaliz&aacute;cia bežn&eacute;ho zisku</strong></em>&nbsp;- podnik uprednostňuje aktu&aacute;lny efekt pred dlhodobou prosperitou. To znamen&aacute;, že chce zv&yacute;&scaron;iť&nbsp; tržby z&nbsp;predaja bicyklov a&nbsp;nechce sa p&uacute;&scaron;ťať do predaja pr&iacute;lb</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0.86em 0px 1.3em; padding: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #343131; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13px;\"><em style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; zoom: 1;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; zoom: 1;\">3.&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;Maximaliz&aacute;cia trhov&eacute;ho podielu</strong></em>&nbsp;- snaha podniku z&iacute;skať dopredu vytyčen&yacute; trhov&yacute; podiel znižovan&iacute;m cien. To znamen&aacute;, že podnik vzhľadom na to, že si chce z&iacute;skať z&aacute;kazn&iacute;kov</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0.86em 0px 1.3em; padding: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #343131; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13px;\"><em style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; zoom: 1;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; zoom: 1;\">4.&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;Vodcovstvo v&nbsp;oblasti kvality produktov</strong></em>&nbsp;-&nbsp; podnik sa snaž&iacute; poskytovať čo najkvalitnej&scaron;ie produkty a&nbsp;služby.</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0.86em 0px 1.3em; padding: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #343131; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13px;\"><em style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; zoom: 1;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; zoom: 1;\">5.&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;Zisk</strong></em>&nbsp;- je kladn&yacute; rozdiel medzi celkov&yacute;mi v&yacute;nosmi a&nbsp;celkov&yacute;mi n&aacute;kladmi</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0.86em 0px 1.3em; padding: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #343131; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13px;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; zoom: 1;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; Strat&eacute;giu maximaliz&aacute;cie zisku m&ocirc;žeme uskutočniť dvojak&yacute;m sp&ocirc;sobom:</strong></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0.86em 0px 1.3em; padding: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #343131; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13px;\"><em style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; zoom: 1;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; zoom: 1;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;o&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;Strat&eacute;gia vysok&yacute;ch cien</strong></em>&nbsp;- &nbsp;&nbsp;spočiatku v&yacute;robcovia pred&aacute;vaj&uacute; dan&yacute; v&yacute;robok za 10 eur, nesk&ocirc;r 2. v&yacute;robca&nbsp; zn&iacute;ži&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;cenu v&yacute;robku&nbsp; o&nbsp;20 centov a&nbsp;t&yacute;m p&aacute;dom odlak&aacute; z&aacute;kazn&iacute;kov od 1. v&yacute;robcu &nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0.86em 0px 1.3em; padding: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #343131; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13px;\"><em style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; zoom: 1;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; zoom: 1;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;o&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;Strat&eacute;gia minim&aacute;lnych n&aacute;kladov</strong></em>&nbsp;- &nbsp;t&aacute;to strat&eacute;gia m&ocirc;že znamenať zastaranie technick&eacute;ho vybavenia&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0.86em 0px 1.3em; padding: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #343131; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13px;\"><em style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; zoom: 1;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; zoom: 1;\">6.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; N&aacute;vratnosť invest&iacute;ci&iacute;</strong></em>&nbsp;- Tento marketingov&yacute; cieľ sa využ&iacute;va v&nbsp;akciovej spoločnosti, kde akcioniari veria, že vložen&yacute; kapit&aacute;l im prinesie čo najvy&scaron;&scaron;&iacute; zisk.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0.86em 0px 1.3em; padding: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #343131; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13px;\"><em style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; zoom: 1;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; zoom: 1;\">7.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Objem predaja</strong></em>&nbsp;- vych&aacute;dza z&nbsp;predpokladu, že zv&yacute;&scaron;enie v&yacute;roby sp&ocirc;sob&iacute; niž&scaron;ie v&yacute;robn&eacute; n&aacute;klady a&nbsp;t&yacute;m sa dosiahne vy&scaron;&scaron;&iacute; zisk. &nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0.86em 0px 1.3em; padding: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #343131; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13px;\"><em style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; zoom: 1;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; zoom: 1;\">8.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Trhov&yacute; podiel</strong></em>&nbsp;-&nbsp; je percentu&aacute;lne vyjadrenie objemu predaja v&nbsp;porovnan&iacute; s&nbsp;najvy&scaron;&scaron;&iacute;m konkurentom, napr. Jednota v&nbsp;Žiline sa porovn&aacute;va s&nbsp;Jednotou v&nbsp;Bratislave. &nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0.86em 0px 1.3em; padding: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #343131; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13px;\"><em style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; zoom: 1;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; zoom: 1;\">9.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Stabiliz&aacute;cia poz&iacute;cie podniku&nbsp;</strong></em>&nbsp;- T&aacute;to strat&eacute;gia sa využ&iacute;va, keď podnik neprež&iacute;va pr&iacute;li&scaron; najlep&scaron;ie časy napr. je pr&iacute;li&scaron; zadlžen&yacute;.</p>\r\n<h4 style=\"margin: 1.3em 0px 0px; padding: 0px; zoom: 1; font-weight: normal; line-height: 1.3em; font-size: 1.5em; color: #343131; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; zoom: 1;\">B)&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Strat&eacute;gia marketingov&eacute;ho mixu</strong></h4>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0.86em 0px 1.3em; padding: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #343131; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13px;\">- rozhodnut&eacute; o&nbsp;cene mus&iacute; byť koordinovan&eacute; s&nbsp;rozhodnutiami o&nbsp;produkte, propag&aacute;cii a&nbsp;distrib&uacute;cii, t.j. rozhodnutie o&nbsp;cene nem&ocirc;že byť v&nbsp;rozpore s&nbsp;rozhodnut&iacute;m o&nbsp;produkte.</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0.86em 0px 1.3em; padding: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #343131; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13px;\">Produkty vo f&aacute;ze uvedenia na trh maj&uacute; zv&auml;č&scaron;a najvy&scaron;&scaron;iu cenu, potom sa v&nbsp;životnom cykle produktu&nbsp; ich cena postupne znižuje. &nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0.86em 0px 1.3em; padding: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #343131; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13px;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; zoom: 1;\">Z&nbsp;hľadiska predaja rozli&scaron;ujeme tieto typy produktov:</strong></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0.86em 0px 1.3em; padding: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #343131; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13px;\"><em style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; zoom: 1;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; zoom: 1;\">o&nbsp;&nbsp; Komplement&aacute;rne produkty</strong></em>&nbsp;- s&uacute; to produkty, ktor&eacute; sa dopĺňaj&uacute; napr. produkt kolesa na bicykli sa dopĺňa s&nbsp;produktom brzdy na bicykli</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0.86em 0px 1.3em; padding: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #343131; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13px;\"><em style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; zoom: 1;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; zoom: 1;\">o&nbsp;&nbsp; Substitučn&eacute; produkty</strong></em>&nbsp;- s&uacute; to produkty, ktor&eacute; sa vyznačuj&uacute; podobn&yacute;m alebo rovnak&yacute;m charakterom a&nbsp;nahr&aacute;dzaj&uacute; existuj&uacute;ci produkt &nbsp;napr. &nbsp;vyn&aacute;lez produktu mobilu nahradil&nbsp;produkt telef&oacute;nu.</p>\r\n<h4 style=\"margin: 1.3em 0px 0px; padding: 0px; zoom: 1; font-weight: normal; line-height: 1.3em; font-size: 1.5em; color: #343131; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; zoom: 1;\">C)&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; N&aacute;klady</strong></h4>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0.86em 0px 1.3em; padding: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #343131; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13px;\">Podnik s&nbsp;najniž&scaron;&iacute;mi n&aacute;kladmi m&ocirc;že stanoviť niž&scaron;ie ceny, čo m&ocirc;že sp&ocirc;sobiť vysok&yacute; zisk. Tieto ceny sa zvy&scaron;uj&uacute; aj kv&ocirc;li infl&aacute;cii.&nbsp; Niekedy podnik m&ocirc;že stanoviť cenu pod &uacute;roveň podnikov&yacute;ch n&aacute;kladov, čo z&nbsp;dlhodob&eacute;ho hľadiska m&ocirc;že znamenať hrozbu.</p>\r\n<h4 style=\"margin: 1.3em 0px 0px; padding: 0px; zoom: 1; font-weight: normal; line-height: 1.3em; font-size: 1.5em; color: #343131; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; zoom: 1;\">D)&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Organiz&aacute;cia cenotvorby</strong></h4>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0.86em 0px 1.3em; padding: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #343131; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13px;\">- definuje kto je zodpovedn&yacute; za určovanie cien v&nbsp;podniku.</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0.86em 0px 1.3em; padding: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #343131; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13px;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h2 style=\"margin: 1.3em 0px 0px; padding: 0px; zoom: 1; font-weight: normal; line-height: 1.3em; font-size: 2em; color: #343131; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; zoom: 1;\">2.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Extern&eacute; faktory stanovenia cien</strong></h2>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0.86em 0px 1.3em; padding: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #343131; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13px;\">Trh a&nbsp;dopyt</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0.86em 0px 1.3em; padding: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #343131; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13px;\">Cena a&nbsp;dopyt</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0.86em 0px 1.3em; padding: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #343131; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13px;\">N&aacute;klady vymedzuj&uacute; doln&uacute; hranicu ceny, pok&yacute;m trh a&nbsp;dopyt vymedzuje horn&uacute; hranicu ceny.&nbsp; Zn&iacute;ženie ceny sp&ocirc;sob&iacute; zv&yacute;&scaron;enie dopytu a&nbsp;naopak zv&yacute;&scaron;enie ceny sp&ocirc;sob&iacute; spravidla zn&iacute;ženie dopyt, plat&iacute; tam tzv. z&aacute;kon klesaj&uacute;ceho dopytu</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0.86em 0px 1.3em; padding: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #343131; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13px;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0.86em 0px 1.3em; padding: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #343131; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13px;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; zoom: 1;\">Cenov&aacute; pružnosť</strong>&nbsp;- vyjadruje percentu&aacute;lne ako sa zmen&iacute; dopyt pri určitej zmene ceny</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0.86em 0px 1.3em; padding: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #343131; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13px;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; zoom: 1;\">Medzi cenov&eacute; pružnosti patria:</strong></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0.86em 0px 1.3em; padding: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #343131; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13px;\"><em style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; zoom: 1;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; zoom: 1;\">o&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;Jednotkov&aacute; pružnosť dopytu</strong></em>&nbsp;- pri 1 % zmene ceny sa dopyt zmen&iacute; o&nbsp;1 %.</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0.86em 0px 1.3em; padding: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #343131; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13px;\"><em style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; zoom: 1;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; zoom: 1;\">o&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;Nepružn&yacute; dopyt</strong></em>&nbsp;- pri 1 % zmene ceny sa dopyt zmen&iacute; o&nbsp;menej ako 1 %.</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0.86em 0px 1.3em; padding: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #343131; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13px;\"><em style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; zoom: 1;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; zoom: 1;\">o&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;Pružn&yacute; dopyt</strong></em>&nbsp;- pri 1 % zmene ceny sa dopyt zmen&iacute; o&nbsp;viac ako 1 %.</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0.86em 0px 1.3em; padding: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #343131; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13px;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0.86em 0px 1.3em; padding: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #343131; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13px;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; zoom: 1;\">Medzi ďal&scaron;ie pružnosti dopytu patria:</strong></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0.86em 0px 1.3em; padding: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #343131; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13px;\"><em style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; zoom: 1;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; zoom: 1;\">o&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;D&ocirc;chodkov&aacute; pružnosť</strong></em>&nbsp;- vyjadruje ako sa zmen&iacute; dopyt pri zmene d&ocirc;chodkov</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0.86em 0px 1.3em; padding: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #343131; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13px;\"><em style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; zoom: 1;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; zoom: 1;\">o&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;Rovnovažn&aacute; pružnosť</strong></em>&nbsp;- je tak&aacute; pružnosť dopytu, aby cena produktov a&nbsp;služieb pre dan&yacute; podnik bola ziskov&aacute;, to znamen&aacute;, že na jednej strane&nbsp; nem&ocirc;žu byť ani vysok&eacute; ceny produktov a&nbsp;služieb, lebo t&yacute;m&nbsp; p&aacute;dom&nbsp; si podnik odlak&aacute; svojich&nbsp; z&aacute;kazn&iacute;kov, ale na druhej strane by nemali byť n&iacute;zke, lebo podnik riskuje, že nebude mať dostatočn&eacute; tržby z&nbsp;predaja tovarov a&nbsp;služieb.</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0.86em 0px 1.3em; padding: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #343131; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13px;\"><em style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; zoom: 1;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; zoom: 1;\">o&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;Tot&aacute;lna pružnosť</strong></em>&nbsp;- podnik by mal mať tak&uacute; pružnosť cien, ak&uacute; maj&uacute; jeho najv&auml;č&scaron;&iacute; konkurenti.</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0.86em 0px 1.3em; padding: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #343131; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13px;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0.86em 0px 1.3em; padding: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #343131; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13px;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; zoom: 1;\">Cena a ponuka</strong></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0.86em 0px 1.3em; padding: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #343131; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13px;\">Ponuka predstavuje množstvo tovarov a&nbsp;služieb, ktor&eacute; s&uacute; ochotn&iacute;&nbsp; predať pred&aacute;vaj&uacute;ci za určit&uacute; cenu.</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0.86em 0px 1.3em; padding: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #343131; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13px;\"><em style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; zoom: 1;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; zoom: 1;\">N&aacute;kladov&aacute; krivka</strong></em>&nbsp;- vyjadruje vzťah medzi n&aacute;kladmi a&nbsp;množstvom vyroben&yacute;ch v&yacute;robkov</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0.86em 0px 1.3em; padding: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #343131; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13px;\"><em style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; zoom: 1;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; zoom: 1;\">Prebytok na trhu</strong></em>&nbsp;&ndash; vznik&aacute; za situ&aacute;cie, keď ponuka je vy&scaron;&scaron;ia ako dopyt.</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0.86em 0px 1.3em; padding: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #343131; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13px;\"><em style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; zoom: 1;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; zoom: 1;\">Nedostatok na trhu</strong></em>&nbsp;- vznik&aacute; za situ&aacute;cie, keď dopyt je vy&scaron;&scaron;&iacute; ako ponuka.</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0.86em 0px 1.3em; padding: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #343131; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13px;\"><em style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; zoom: 1;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; zoom: 1;\">Rovnov&aacute;žny stav na trhu</strong></em>&nbsp;- vznik&aacute; za situ&aacute;cie, keď dopyt sa rovn&aacute; ponuke, tento stav v&nbsp;trhovej ekonomike nenast&aacute;va.</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0.86em 0px 1.3em; padding: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #343131; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13px;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0.86em 0px 1.3em; padding: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #343131; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13px;\">V&nbsp;s&uacute;vislosti s&nbsp;cenou v&nbsp;trhovej ekonomike pozn&aacute;me&nbsp;<strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; zoom: 1;\">dva druhy konkurencie</strong>, a&nbsp;to:</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0.86em 0px 1.3em; padding: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #343131; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13px;\"><em style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; zoom: 1;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; zoom: 1;\">o&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;Cenov&aacute; konkurencia</strong></em>&nbsp;- je to s&uacute;perenie podnikov prostredn&iacute;ctvom manipulovania ceny</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0.86em 0px 1.3em; padding: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #343131; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13px;\"><em style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; zoom: 1;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; zoom: 1;\">o&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;Necenov&aacute; konkurencia</strong></em>&nbsp;- je to s&uacute;perenie podnikov prostredn&iacute;ctvom necenov&yacute;ch faktorov a&nbsp;to napr&iacute;klad&nbsp; zlep&scaron;en&iacute;m &scaron;t&yacute;lu, kvality, značky produktov a&nbsp;služieb</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0.86em 0px 1.3em; padding: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #343131; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13px;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0.86em 0px 1.3em; padding: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #343131; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13px;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; zoom: 1;\">Ostatn&eacute; faktory vonkaj&scaron;ieho prostredia</strong></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0.86em 0px 1.3em; padding: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #343131; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13px;\"><em style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; zoom: 1;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; zoom: 1;\">Ekonomick&eacute; faktory</strong></em>&nbsp;- tam patria infl&aacute;cia, recesia a&nbsp;&uacute;rokov&eacute; sadzby</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0.86em 0px 1.3em; padding: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #343131; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13px;\"><em style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; zoom: 1;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; zoom: 1;\">Požiadavky sprostredkovateľov</strong></em>&nbsp;- tam patria primeran&yacute; zisk, motiv&aacute;cia</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0.86em 0px 1.3em; padding: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #343131; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13px;\"><em style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; zoom: 1;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; zoom: 1;\">&Scaron;t&aacute;tna spr&aacute;va</strong></em>&nbsp;- tam patria napr&iacute;klad nariadenia tykaj&uacute;ce sa regul&aacute;cie cien</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0.86em 0px 1.3em; padding: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #343131; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13px;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0.86em 0px 1.3em; padding: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #343131; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13px;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; zoom: 1;\">Cenov&eacute; strat&eacute;gie:</strong></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0.86em 0px 1.3em; padding: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #343131; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13px;\"><em style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; zoom: 1;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; zoom: 1;\">1.&nbsp; &nbsp;Určovanie cien nov&yacute;ch produktov</strong></em></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0.86em 0px 1.3em; padding: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #343131; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13px;\">A)&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; Určovanie cien inovovan&yacute;ch produktov</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0.86em 0px 1.3em; padding: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #343131; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13px;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; o&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;vysoko v&yacute;nosov&eacute; ceny - tieto ceny možno stanoviť iba za určit&yacute;ch podmienok</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0.86em 0px 1.3em; padding: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #343131; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13px;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; o&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;prienikov&eacute; ceny - sleduj&uacute; zisk trhov&eacute;ho podielu, znižovanie cien a&nbsp;znižovanie cien</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0.86em 0px 1.3em; padding: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #343131; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13px;\">B)&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Cenotvorba limituj&uacute;ceho produktu - postavenie na trhu sa určuje prostredn&iacute;ctvom ceny a&nbsp;kvality produktov a&nbsp;služieb&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0.86em 0px 1.3em; padding: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #343131; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13px;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; zoom: 1;\">2.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Strat&eacute;gie tvorby cien pre produktov&yacute; mix</strong>&nbsp;- hľad&aacute; sa s&uacute;bor cien, ktor&yacute; bude maximalizovať zisk na cel&yacute; produktov&yacute; mix</p>\r\n<h2 style=\"margin: 1.3em 0px 0px; padding: 0px; zoom: 1; font-weight: normal; line-height: 1.3em; font-size: 2em; color: #343131; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; zoom: 1;\">3.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Strat&eacute;gie cenov&yacute;ch &uacute;prav</strong></h2>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0.86em 0px 1.3em; padding: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #343131; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13px;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; zoom: 1;\">Medzi strat&eacute;gie cenov&yacute;ch &uacute;prav patria:</strong></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0.86em 0px 1.3em; padding: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #343131; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13px;\"><em style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; zoom: 1;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; zoom: 1;\">A)&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Cenov&aacute; diferenci&aacute;cia</strong></em>&nbsp;- zohľadnenie rozdielov medzi z&aacute;kazn&iacute;kmi, produktom a&nbsp;miestom. To znamen&aacute;, že in&aacute; cena bude za chlieb ako za maslo</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0.86em 0px 1.3em; padding: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #343131; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13px;\"><em style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; zoom: 1;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; zoom: 1;\">B)&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Psychologicky orientovan&eacute; ceny</strong></em>&nbsp;- s&uacute; to ceny produktov a&nbsp;služieb, ktor&eacute; končia 9-kou napr. chlieb za 0,99 eura.</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0.86em 0px 1.3em; padding: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #343131; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13px;\"><em style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; zoom: 1;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; zoom: 1;\">C)&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Akčn&eacute; ceny&nbsp;</strong></em>- dočasn&eacute; niž&scaron;ie oceňovanie produktov</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0.86em 0px 1.3em; padding: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #343131; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13px;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0.86em 0px 1.3em; padding: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #343131; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13px;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; zoom: 1;\">Chyby pri určovan&iacute; cien:</strong></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0.86em 0px 1.3em; padding: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #343131; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13px;\"><em style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; zoom: 1;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; zoom: 1;\">1.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Pr&iacute;li&scaron; n&aacute;kladov&aacute; orient&aacute;cia tvorby cien</strong></em>&nbsp;- podnik pr&iacute;li&scaron; prihliada pri tvorbe cien&nbsp; na v&yacute;&scaron;ku n&aacute;kladov v&nbsp;podniku&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0.86em 0px 1.3em; padding: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #343131; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13px;\"><em style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; zoom: 1;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; zoom: 1;\">2.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Neprejavovanie&nbsp; sez&oacute;nnosti cien</strong></em>&nbsp;- &nbsp;podnik nie je schopn&yacute; prisp&ocirc;sobiť ceny podľa sez&oacute;ny &nbsp;&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0.86em 0px 1.3em; padding: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #343131; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13px;\"><em style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; zoom: 1;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; zoom: 1;\">3.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Neprejavovanie zmien na trhu</strong></em>&nbsp;- podnik nie je schopn&yacute; reagovať na spr&aacute;vanie konkurentov z&nbsp;hľadiska tvorby cien &nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0.86em 0px 1.3em; padding: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #343131; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13px;\"><em style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; zoom: 1;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; zoom: 1;\">4.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Nemožnosť reakcie na ostatn&eacute; prvky marketingov&eacute;ho mixu&nbsp;&nbsp;</strong></em></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0.86em 0px 1.3em; padding: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #343131; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13px;\"><em style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; zoom: 1;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; zoom: 1;\">5.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Nedostatočn&aacute; diferenci&aacute;cia ceny produktov</strong></em>&nbsp;- podnik nie je dostatočne schopn&yacute; reagovať na rozdielnosť kvality svojich produktov&nbsp; &nbsp;</p>');

